title: సొంత ప్రజలకే అవకాశాలు ఇవ్వాలనే తమిళ చిత్ర పరిశ్రమ ఆలోచన ధోరణి మారాలి: పవన్‌ కల్యాణ్
content: తమిళ సినిమాల్లో పని చేసేవారు తమిళులై ఉండాలని కోలీవుడ్‌ చిత్ర పరిశ్రమ తీసుకొచ్చిన నిబంధనపై ‘బ్రో’ ప్రీ రిలీజ్ ఈవెంట్‌లో సినీ నటుడు పవన్‌ కల్యాణ్ మాట్లాడారు. “మన పరిశ్రమలో మన వాళ్లే పని చేయాలన్న ఆలోచన ధోరణి నుంచి తమిళ చిత్ర పరిశ్రమ బయటికి రావాలి. అన్ని భాషల వాళ్లు ఉంటేనే అది సినిమా అవుతుంది. తమిళ చిత్ర పరిశ్రమ కూడా ‘RRR’ లాంటి గొప్ప సినిమాలు తీయాలని కోరుకుంటున్నా,’’ అని పవన్‌ కల్యాణ్ అన్నారు.
author: 6460731b8f69d20007900c03

title: LS passes Bill to decriminalise minor offences by amending 42 laws
content: The Lok Sabha has passed the Jan Vishwas (Amendment of Provisions) Bill, 2023 which will decriminalise minor offences by amending over 180 provisions under 42 laws. Union Minister Piyush Goyal said that the Bill will promote ease of doing business. In the Bill, several fines are converted to penalties and imprisonment is removed as a punishment for many offences.
author: 5f70e895d43821580e6d708c

title: Ex-Indian-origin minister Tharman launches Prez bid in Singapore
content: Singapore's former Indian-origin minister Tharman Shanmugaratnam formally launched his presidential bid on Wednesday, pledging to evolve Singapore's culture to keep it a \shining spot\" in the world. Tharman stepped down from active politics after 22 years last month. Singapore's Presidential polls will be held in September this year as President Halimah Yacob's term ends on September 13."
author: 618260ec573ea259f930fff5

title: Florida ocean temperatures cross 100°F, could be a record high
content: Surface ocean temperature around the Florida Keys reached 101.19°F (38.43°C) this week, making the water as hot as a hot tub and potentially breaking the world heat record. Other nearby buoys also surpassed 100°F and 90°F. According to the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA), normal ocean temperatures in the area around this time should range from 73°F to 88°F.
author: 61cc1f6b573ea24b755b307a

title: ₹55 lakh loss due to stone pelting on Vande Bharat trains: Govt
content: Union Minister Ashwini Vaishnaw on Wednesday said that the Indian Railways have incurred a loss of ₹55.60 lakh over the last five years due to damage caused by stone pelting on Vande Bharat trains. Vaishnaw said that in order to safeguard the lives of passengers, 'OPERATION SATHI' is being conducted to sensitise people against stone pelting and its consequences.
author: 61de9224d438211e6ea8e7d5

content: Minister of State for Home Nityanand Rai said after the abrogation of Article 370 in 2019, nearly 30,000 vacancies were filled in Jammu and Kashmir. Speaking in Rajya Sabha, Rai said, \Recruiting agencies have advertised 7

title: कौन-कौनसे भारतीय प्रधानमंत्रियों को अविश्वास प्रस्ताव के कारण देना पड़ा है इस्तीफा?
content: संसद में अब तक 27 बार अविश्वास प्रस्ताव लाया गया है जिनमें से 3 अविश्वास प्रस्तावों के परिणामस्वरूप प्रधानमंत्री को इस्तीफा देना पड़ा है। 1990 में तत्कालीन प्रधानमंत्री वीपी सिंह को जबकि 1997 में एचडी देवगौड़ा को इस्तीफा देना पड़ा था। वहीं, 1999 में बहुमत साबित नहीं कर पाने के कारण अटल बिहारी वाजपेयी को इस्तीफा देना पड़ा था।
author: 62bec075573ea25553962618

title: ఫిర్యాదుపై స్పందించలేదని హైదరాబాద్‌లోని జీహెచ్‌ఎంసీ వార్డ్‌ ఆఫీస్‌లో అధికారి టేబుల్‌పై పామును వదిలిన యువకుడు
content: సంపత్ కుమార్ అనే యువకుడు తన ఇంట్లోకి వచ్చిన పాముని పట్టుకుని తీసుకెళ్లి హైదరాబాద్ శివారులోని అల్వాల్‌ జీహెచ్‌ఎంసీ వార్డు కార్యాలయంలో ఓ అధికారి టేబుల్‌పై వదిలిపెట్టాడు. అంతకుముందు వరద నీరు వల్ల ఇంట్లోకి పాములు వస్తున్నాయని అతను హెల్ప్‌లైన్‌కి ఫోన్ చేశాడు. 6 గంటలు గడిచినా అధికారులు పట్టించుకోకపోవడంతో అసహనంతో పామును ఆఫీసుకి తీసుకెళ్లాడు. సంపత్ చేసిన పనికి జీహెచ్ఎంసీ అధికారులు షాక్‌ అయ్యారు.
author: 6460731b8f69d20007900c03

title: క్యాబ్‌, మెట్రోతో సహా అన్ని వాహనాల్లో ప్రయాణానికి ఒకే కార్డును తీసుకురానున్న తెలంగాణ ప్రభుత్వం
content: హైదరాబాద్‌లో మెట్రో రైలు నుంచి ఆటోల వరకు అన్ని ప్రభుత్వ, ప్రైవేట్‌ వాహనాల్లో ప్రయాణాన్ని సులభతరం చేసేందుకు కామన్ మొబిలిటీ కార్డులను తీసుకురావాలని తెలంగాణ ప్రభుత్వం భావిస్తోంది. ఈ కార్డును ప్రయోగాత్మకంగా ఆగస్టు రెండో వారంలోగా నగర పౌరులకు అందుబాటులోకి తేవాలని అధికారులను మంత్రులు కేటీఆర్, పువ్వాడ అజయ్ ఆదేశించారు. మొదట మెట్రో, ఆర్టీసీ బస్సులో ప్రయాణానికి వీలుగా ఈ కార్డుని జారీ చేస్తామని తెలిపారు.
author: 6460731b8f69d20007900c03

title: ములుగు జిల్లాలోని అడవిలో చిక్కుకున్న 80 మంది పర్యాటకులను రాత్రంతా శ్రమించి కాపాడిన అధికారులు
content: ములుగు జిల్లాలోని ముత్యంధార జలపాతం సందర్శనకు వెళ్లి వీరభద్రవరం అడవుల్లో చిక్కుకున్న పర్యాటకులను రెస్క్యూ టీమ్‌లు, పోలీసులు కాపాడారు. రాత్రి వేళ దాదాపు 8 గంటలు శ్రమించి వారిని సురక్షితంగా అక్కడి నుంచి తరలించారు. ‘’18-25 ఏళ్ల వయస్సున్న మొత్తం 80 మంది పురుషులు పొరుగు జిల్లాల నుంచి పర్యటనకు వచ్చి చిక్కుకున్నారు. ఉదయం 3:30 గంటల సమయానికి వారందరినీ రక్షించాం,’’ అని జిల్లా అధికారులు తెలిపారు.
author: 6460731b8f69d20007900c03

title: અવિશ્વાસ પ્રસ્તાવને કારણે ભારતના કયા વડાપ્રધાનોએ રાજીનામું આપવું પડ્યું?
content: સંસદમાં અત્યાર સુધીમાં 27 વાર અવિશ્વાસની દરખાસ્ત લાવવામાં આવી છે જેમાંથી 3 અવિશ્વાસની દરખાસ્તના કારણે વડાપ્રધાને રાજીનામું આપ્યું છે. 1990માં તત્કાલિન વડાપ્રધાન વીપી સિંહે જ્યારે 1997માં એચડી દેવગૌડાએ રાજીનામું આપવું પડ્યું હતું. 1999માં બહુમત સાબિત ન કરી શકવાના કારણે અટલ બિહારી બાજપેયીએ રાજીનામું આપવું પડ્યું હતું.
author: 64a11524e1142b00074d12be

title: અમદાવાદમાં યોજાનારી ભારત-પાકની વર્લ્ડકપ મેચની નવરાત્રીને કારણે રીશેડ્યુલની શક્યતા: અહેવાલ
content: અહેવાલ અનુસાર, અમદાવાદમાં 15 ઓક્ટોબરે યોજાનારી ભારત-પાકિસ્તાન વર્લ્ડકપની મેચને રીશેડ્યુલ કરવામાં આવે તેવી શક્યતા છે. 15 ઓક્ટોબરે નવરાત્રીનો પણ પ્રારંભ થતો હોવાથી તેને ધ્યાનમાં રાખીને સુરક્ષા એજન્સીઓએ કથિત રીતે BCCIને આ દિવસે મેચ ના યોજવાની સલાહ આપી છે. નોંધનીય છે, ક્રિકેટ રસિકોએ મેચને લઈ અમદાવાદમાં હોટલ રૂમનું મોટી માત્રામાં બુકિંગ કર્યું છે.
author: 64a11524e1142b00074d12be

title: ನವರಾತ್ರಿ ಆರಂಭದ ದಿನವೇ ನಿಗದಿಯಾಗಿದ್ದ ಭಾರತ-ಪಾಕ್ WC ಪಂದ್ಯ ಮರು ನಿಗದಿ ಸಾಧ್ಯತೆ: ವರದಿ
content: ಅಕ್ಟೋಬರ್ 15 ರಂದು ಅಹಮದಾಬಾದ್‌ನಲ್ಲಿ ನಿಗದಿಯಾಗಿರುವ ಭಾರತ-ಪಾಕಿಸ್ತಾನ ವಿಶ್ವಕಪ್ ಪಂದ್ಯವನ್ನು ಮರು ನಿಗದಿಪಡಿಸುವ ಸಾಧ್ಯತೆಯಿದೆ ಎಂದು ವರದಿಗಳು ತಿಳಿಸಿವೆ. ನವರಾತ್ರಿ ಉತ್ಸವದ ಆರಂಭದ ದಿನ ಆಗಿರುವುದರಿಂದ ಅಂದು ಗುಜರಾತ್‌ನಾದ್ಯಂತ ಜನರು ರಾತ್ರಿ ಗರ್ಭಾ ಕಾರ್ಯಕ್ರಮಗಳಲ್ಲಿ ಸಾಮೂಹಿಕವಾಗಿ ಭಾಗವಹಿಸುತ್ತಾರೆ. ಈ ಕಾರಣ ಪಂದ್ಯ ಮರುನಿಗದಿ ಮಾಡುವ ಅಗತ್ಯವಿದೆ ಎಂದು ಭದ್ರತಾ ಏಜೆನ್ಸಿಗಳು ಬಿಸಿಸಿಐಗೆ ಸಲಹೆ ನೀಡಿವೆ ಎಂದು ವರದಿಯಾಗಿದೆ.
author: 64a11562d7301500079ed581

title: BRS gives no-confidence motion notice in LS, YSRCP to oppose move
content: Bharat Rashtra Samithi (BRS) has moved a no-confidence motion notice against the PM Narendra Modi-led government in the Lok Sabha. This comes as the 26 Opposition parties' alliance, INDIA, also moved the notice in the House. However, YSRCP MP Vijayasai Reddy V has questioned the necessity of the motion and said that his party will oppose it.
author: 5f70e895d43821580e6d708c

title: In a 1st, JD(U) issues whip to RS Dy Chairman over Delhi ordinance
content: The Janata Dal (United) has issued a whip to Rajya Sabha Deputy Chairman and party MP Harivansh for the first time in his tenure to support the party's stand of opposing the Centre's ordinance over control of services in Delhi. Harivansh was re-elected as the Rajya Sabha Deputy Chairman in 2020 while JD(U) was still in an alliance with BJP.
author: 5f70e895d43821580e6d708c

title: Centre moves SC seeking extension of ED chief SK Mishra's term
content: The central government has moved the Supreme Court seeking an extension of term for Enforcement Directorate (ED) chief SK Mishra. This comes after the apex court called the third extension granted to Mishra \illegal\" but allowed him to continue on the post till July 31. \"Can one person be so indispensable?\" the apex court had earlier said."
author: 5f70e895d43821580e6d708c

title: 80 tourists get stranded at waterfall in Telangana, rescued
content: As many as 80 tourists who got stranded at Muthyala Dhara waterfall after the water flow increased on Wednesday in Telangana's Mulugu have been rescued, the district's SP said. The SP added that one boy was treated after he was bitten by a scorpion. \We verified with every group and no one is left behind now
author: NEWS

title: SC allows ED chief Sanjay Kumar Mishra to remain at post till Sep 15
content: The Supreme Court on Thursday allowed Enforcement Directorate (ED) chief Sanjay Kumar Mishra to remain at the post till September 15. Centre had sought a tenure extension till October 15 in view of the ongoing Financial Action Task Force review. Defending the third extension granted to him, Centre had said, \This officer isn't some DGP...but an officer representing the country.\""
author: 60ae2b15573ea27d7e496a9f

title: Indian Oil gas pipeline bursts in Yamuna river in UP, viral video shows water erupting
content: An underwater gas pipeline of Indian Oil burst in the Yamuna river in the Bagpat district of Uttar Pradesh, a video of which surfaced online on Wednesday. Confirming that the pipeline belonged to Indian Oil, Baraut SDM Subhash Singh said, \The Panipat-Dadri gas pipeline had a leakage. I contacted the concerned department and the valves were closed...Slowly
author: NEWS

title: Man kills wife & her parents, goes to police station with 9-month-old baby in Assam
content: A 25-year-old man, identified as Nazibur Rahman, allegedly murdered his wife Sanghamitra Ghosh and her parents Sanjib Ghosh and Junu Ghosh in Assam's Golaghat town. Rahman visited the police station with his nine-month-old baby to surrender. \He confessed that he had committed the crime
newsType: \" police said. Nazibur and Sanghamitra met online in 2020 and eloped to get married
author: police added."

title: No-confidence motion against government accepted by Lok Sabha Speaker Om Birla
content: Lok Sabha Speaker Om Birla on Wednesday allowed a no-confidence motion moved by the Congress against PM Narendra Modi-led government. \I will discuss this with the leaders of all parties and inform you of an appropriate time to take this up for discussion
author: the Opposition has been demanding that PM Modi should speak on the Manipur issue."

title: Seems speaking on Manipur will hurt PM's prestige: Kharge to Shah
content: Leader of Opposition in Rajya Sabha Mallikarjun Kharge wrote letter to Union Home Minister Amit Shah over protest in Parliament on Manipur issue. \We have been urging PM to come and speak in Parliament but it seems it will hurt his prestige. We are committed to people of this country and we will pay any price for it
author: NEWS

title: Latest drone visuals show flooding in Greater Noida's Ecotech 3
content: Flooding was reported in low lying areas of Noida and Greater Noida following increase in water level of Hindon River. Several vehicles were submerged in water near Ecotech 3. Two electric substations were also submerged in water, disrupting electricity supply in Ghaziabad's Raj Nagar extension. More than 200 people have been evacuated and shifted to shelter homes.
author: 61b9bdfdd4382131e00cad4e

title: PM Modi inaugurates redeveloped ITPO complex in Delhi
content: PM Narendra Modi on Wednesday inaugurated the India Trade Promotion Organisation (ITPO) complex in Delhi's Pragati Maidan. The G-20 leaders' meeting in September will be held in this complex which has a campus area of 123 acres. The complex, built at a cost of over ₹2,700 crore,  is ranked among the top 10 exhibition and convention complexes in the world.
author: 61b9bdfdd4382131e00cad4e

title: Delhi-NCR receive heavy rainfall; waterlogging reported at ITO
content: Rainfall lashed parts of Delhi-NCR on Wednesday morning, causing waterlogging in several areas including ITO. The vehicular traffic was also affected due to lack of visibility on the roads. Meanwhile, the schools in Noida will stay shut today. Yamuna River continued to overflow in Delhi with water level recorded at 205.45 meters on Tuesday morning.
author: 61b9bdfdd4382131e00cad4e

title: India will be among world's top 3 economies in my 3rd term: PM
content: While speaking at the inauguration of the IECC Complex in Delhi's Pragati Maidan, PM Narendra Modi said India will be among the top three economies of the world in his third term. He said India ranked 10th on the list of world economies when BJP came to power in 2014 and became the fifth biggest economy in his second term.

He said India ranked 10th on the list of world economies when BJP came to power in 2014 and became the fifth biggest economy in his second term.

title: हम फिल्में प्रोमोट करते हैं लेकिन इसने हमें प्रोमोट किया: कावाला गाना ट्रेंड करने पर तमन्ना
content: ऐक्ट्रेस तमन्ना भाटिया ने आगामी फिल्म 'जेलर' के गाने 'कावाला' के ट्रेंड करने को लेकर कहा, \आमतौर पर हम फिल्में प्रोमोट करते हैं लेकिन इस गाने ने हमें प्रोमोट किया है।\" उन्होंने कहा
newsType: \"लोगों ने इसे बहुत प्यार दिया और यह खूब ट्रेंड कर रहा है।\" गौरतलब है
author: 'कावाला' का हिंदी वर्ज़न 'तू आ दिलबरा' गुरुवार को लॉन्च किया गया।"

title: ईडी की छापेमारी के बाद निवेशकों के साथ कॉल पर रो पड़े थे बायजू के सीईओ रवींद्रन: रिपोर्ट
content: ब्लूमबर्ग की रिपोर्ट के अनुसार, अप्रैल के अंत में बेंगलुरु स्थित परिसरों पर ईडी की छापेमारी के बाद शीर्ष निवेशकों के साथ कॉल पर अपनी कंपनी का बचाव करते समय एडटेक स्टार्टअप बायजू के सीईओ बायजू रवींद्रन रो पड़े थे। रिपोर्ट में कहा गया है कि उस वक्त वह दुबई में थे। छापेमारी फेमा के उल्लंघन को लेकर हुई थी।
author: 5f70e895d43821580e6d7076

title: BYJU'S CEO broke down on calls with investors after ED raids: Report
content: Edtech startup BYJU's CEO Byju Raveendran broke down in tears while defending his company on calls with top investors after its premises in Bengaluru were raided by the Enforcement Directorate in late April, Bloomberg reported. He was in Dubai, paced up and down in his condo and kept drinking black coffee, the report added. BYJU's was raided under FEMA Act.
author: 60ae2b15573ea27d7e496a9f

title: Netweb Technologies lists at 89.4% premium over issue price on NSE
content: Shares of Netweb Technologies listed at an 89.4% premium on Nifty over their issue price of ₹500/share on Thursday. They listed at ₹947/share on Nifty and at ₹942.5/share on Sensex, which marked an 88.5% premium. With an mcap of over ₹5,080 crore, Netweb's shares were trading at ₹907.5/share at around 11:30 am on Sensex after touching a high of ₹953/share.
author: 61a77175d43821182161b35e

title: Adani Group adds ₹50,606 crore to m-cap in 1 day on Tuesday
content: Billionaire Gautam Adani-led Adani Group added ₹50,606 crore to its m-cap in one day on Tuesday. The m-cap of the 10 Adani Group firms stood at around ₹10.6 lakh crore on Tuesday as against ₹10.1 lakh crore on Monday, \bringing a windfall gain for its shareholders\"
newsType: the conglomerate said. The top gainers were Adani Green Energy and Adani Total Gas."
author: NEWS

title: I-T Dept's seized assets rose 52% YoY in FY23 to ₹1,766 cr: Govt
content: Number of groups searched and assets seized by Income Tax Department has risen over previous three fiscals, according to data provided by MoS Finance Pankaj Chaudhary. In FY23, 741 groups were raided and assets worth ₹1,765.56 crore were seized, a 52% YoY rise from assets worth ₹1,159.56 crore seized in FY22. In FY21, assets worth ₹880.83 crore were seized.

title: 169 Jet Airways workmen who worked over 240 days to be reinstated
content: The Supreme Court has ordered reinstatement of 169 workmen to Jet Airways as they'd worked for over 240 days at the airline. A dispute had arisen over non-renewal of workmen's fixed-term contracts. Workmen who've worked for 240 days \would be entitled to be made permanent and no contract/settlement which abridges such a right can be agreed upon\"
author: NEWS

title: ನೋಯ್ಡಾದ ಇಕೋಟೆಕ್ 3ರಲ್ಲಿ ಪ್ರವಾಹದ ದೃಶ್ಯ ಡ್ರೋನ್‌ನಲ್ಲಿ ಸೆರೆ
content: ಹಿಂಡನ್ ನದಿಯ ನೀರಿನ ಮಟ್ಟದಲ್ಲಿ ಹೆಚ್ಚಳವಾದ ಹಿನ್ನೆಲೆ ನೋಯ್ಡಾ ಮತ್ತು ಗ್ರೇಟರ್ ನೋಯ್ಡಾದ ತಗ್ಗು ಪ್ರದೇಶಗಳಲ್ಲಿ ಪ್ರವಾಹ ಉಂಟಾದ ಬಗ್ಗೆ ವರದಿಯಾಗಿದೆ. ಇಕೋಟೆಕ್- 3ರ ಬಳಿ ಹಲವಾರು ವಾಹನಗಳು ಮುಳುಗಿದ್ದು, ಎರಡು ವಿದ್ಯುತ್ ಸಬ್‌ಸ್ಟೇಷನ್‌ಗಳು ಸಹ ನೀರಿನಲ್ಲಿ ಮುಳುಗಡೆಯಾಗಿವೆ. ಗಾಜಿಯಾಬಾದ್‌ನ ರಾಜ್ ನಗರ ಎಕ್ಸ್‌ಟೆನ್ಷನ್‌ನಲ್ಲಿ ವಿದ್ಯುತ್ ಪೂರೈಕೆ ಅಡಚಣೆಯಾಗಿದೆ. 200ಕ್ಕೂ ಹೆಚ್ಚು ಜನರನ್ನು ಆಶ್ರಯ ಮನೆಗಳಿಗೆ ಸ್ಥಳಾಂತರ ಮಾಡಲಾಗಿದೆ
author: 64a51b9a095ebc00070d3cde

title: ಸೆ.15ರವರೆಗೆ ಇಡಿ ಮುಖ್ಯಸ್ಥ ಸಂಜಯ್ ಕುಮಾರ್ ಮಿಶ್ರಾ ಹುದ್ದೆಯಲ್ಲಿರಲು ಸುಪ್ರೀಂ ಕೋರ್ಟ್ ಅನುಮತಿ
content: ಜಾರಿ ನಿರ್ದೇಶನಾಲಯ (ಇಡಿ) ಮುಖ್ಯಸ್ಥ ಸಂಜಯ್ ಕುಮಾರ್ ಮಿಶ್ರಾರನ್ನು ಸೆಪ್ಟೆಂಬರ್ 15ರವರೆಗೆ ಹುದ್ದೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ಉಳಿಯಲು ಸುಪ್ರೀಂ ಕೋರ್ಟ್ ಗುರುವಾರ ಅನುಮತಿ ನೀಡಿದೆ. ಸದ್ಯ ನಡೆಯುತ್ತಿರುವ ಹಣಕಾಸು ಆ್ಯಕ್ಷನ್ ಟಾಸ್ಕ್ ಫೋರ್ಸ್ ಪರಿಶೀಲನೆಯನ್ನು ಗಮನದಲ್ಲಿರಿಸಿ ಅಕ್ಟೋಬರ್ 15ರವರೆಗೆ ಅಧಿಕಾರಾವಧಿಯನ್ನು ವಿಸ್ತರಿಸುವಂತೆ ಕೇಂದ್ರ ಕೋರಿತ್ತು. ಮೂರನೇ ವಿಸ್ತರಣೆಯನ್ನು ಸಮರ್ಥಿಸಿಕೊಂಡ ಕೇಂದ್ರ, \ಇವರು ದೇಶವನ್ನು ಪ್ರತಿನಿಧಿಸುವ ಅಧಿಕಾರಿ
author: NEWS

title: ಅಲಹಾಬಾದ್ ಹೈಕೋರ್ಟ್ ತೀರ್ಪನ್ನು ಕಾಯ್ದಿರಿಸಿದ್ದರಿಂದ ಜ್ಞಾನವಾಪಿ ಸಮೀಕ್ಷೆಯನ್ನು ಆಗಸ್ಟ್ 3 ರವರೆಗೆ ಸ್ಥಗಿತ
content: ಉತ್ತರ ಪ್ರದೇಶದ ವಾರಣಾಸಿಯಲ್ಲಿರುವ ಜ್ಞಾನವಾಪಿ ಮಸೀದಿಯ ವೈಜ್ಞಾನಿಕ ಸಮೀಕ್ಷೆಗೆ ಅಲಹಾಬಾದ್ ಹೈಕೋರ್ಟ್ ಗುರುವಾರ ತಡೆಯಾಜ್ಞೆ ನೀಡಿದ್ದು, ಆಗಸ್ಟ್ 3ರವರೆಗೆ ತನ್ನ ಆದೇಶವನ್ನು ಕಾಯ್ದಿರಿಸಿದೆ. ಭಾರತೀಯ ಪುರಾತತ್ವ ಸರ್ವೇಕ್ಷಣಾ ಇಲಾಖೆಯಿಂದ ಸಮೀಕ್ಷೆ ನಡೆಯಲಿದ್ದು, ಜುಲೈ 26ರ ಸಂಜೆ 5ರವರೆಗೆ ಸುಪ್ರೀಂ ಕೋರ್ಟ್ ತಡೆ ನೀಡಿತ್ತು.
author: 64a51b9a095ebc00070d3cde

title: 3 ದಶಕಗಳ ನಂತರ ಶ್ರೀನಗರದಲ್ಲಿ ನಡೆದ ಮೊಹರಂ ಮೆರವಣಿಗೆ
content: 3 ದಶಕಗಳ ನಿಷೇಧದ ನಂತರ ಜಮ್ಮು ಮತ್ತು ಕಾಶ್ಮೀರ ಆಡಳಿತವು ಗುರುವಾರ ಶ್ರೀನಗರದಲ್ಲಿ ಸಾಂಪ್ರದಾಯಿಕ ಮಾರ್ಗದ ಮೂಲಕ 8ನೇ ಮೊಹರಂ ಮೆರವಣಿಗೆಗೆ ಅವಕಾಶ ನೀಡಿದೆ. ಮೆರವಣಿಗೆಯ ವಿಡಿಯೋ ಆನ್‌ಲೈನ್‌ನಲ್ಲಿ ಹರಿದಾಡುತ್ತಿದೆ. ಬೆಳಿಗ್ಗೆ 6ರಿಂದ 8ರವರೆಗೆ  ಮೆರವಣಿಗೆ ನಡೆಸಲು ಸ್ಥಳೀಯ ಆಡಳಿತವು ಸಮಯದ ಮಿತಿ ನಿಗದಿಪಡಿಸಿತ್ತು.
author: 64a51be0095ebc00070d3d33

title: ವೆಸ್ಟ್ ಇಂಡೀಸ್ ವಿರುದ್ಧದ ಮೊದಲ ಏಕದಿನ ಪಂದ್ಯಕ್ಕೆ ಪ್ಲೇಯಿಂಗ್ ಇಲೆವೆನ್‌ ಪ್ರಕಟಿಸಿದ ಭಾರತ
content: ವೆಸ್ಟ್ ಇಂಡೀಸ್ ವಿರುದ್ಧ ಬಾರ್ಬಡೋಸ್‌ನಲ್ಲಿ ನಡೆಯುತ್ತಿರುವ ಮೊದಲ ಏಕದಿನ ಪಂದ್ಯದಲ್ಲಿ ಟಾಸ್ ಗೆದ್ದ ಟೀಂ ಇಂಡಿಯಾ ನಾಯಕ ರೋಹಿತ್ ಶರ್ಮಾ ಬೌಲಿಂಗ್ ಆಯ್ಕೆ ಮಾಡಿಕೊಂಡಿದ್ದಾರೆ. ವೇಗದ ಬೌಲರ್ ಮುಖೇಶ್ ಕುಮಾರ್ ಏಕದಿನ ಕ್ರಿಕೆಟ್‌ಗೆ ಪಾದಾರ್ಪಣೆ ಮಾಡುತ್ತಿದ್ದು, ಭಾರತದ ಪ್ಲೇಯಿಂಗ್ ಇಲೆವೆನ್‌ನಲ್ಲಿ ಶಾರ್ದೂಲ್ ಠಾಕೂರ್, ಉಮ್ರಾನ್ ಮಲಿಕ್ ಮತ್ತು ಕುಲ್ದೀಪ್ ಯಾದವ್ ಸ್ಥಾನ ಪಡೆದಿದ್ದಾರೆ. ಈ ಪಂದ್ಯದಲ್ಲಿ ಭಾರತದ ಪರ ಇಶಾನ್ ಕಿಶನ್ ವಿಕೆಟ್ ಕೀಪಿಂಗ್ ಮಾಡಲಿದ್ದಾರೆ.
author: 64a51be0095ebc00070d3d33

title: ಪ್ರಧಾನಿ ಮೋದಿ ಮತ್ತು ಆದಿತ್ಯನಾಥ್ ಅವರ​ ಆಧಾರ್​ ಕಾರ್ಡ್​ ತಿರುಚಿ ಜನ್ಮ ದಿನಾಂಕ ಬದಲಾವಣೆ
content: ಪ್ರಧಾನಮಂತ್ರಿ ನರೇಂದ್ರ ಮೋದಿ ಹಾಗೂ ಉತ್ತರ ಪ್ರದೇಶ ಮುಖ್ಯಮಂತ್ರಿ ಯೋಗಿ ಆದಿತ್ಯನಾಥ್ ಅವರ ಆಧಾರ್ ಕಾರ್ಡ್ ತಿರುಚಿದ ಆರೋಪದ ಮೇಲೆ ಬಿಹಾರದ ಮುಜಾಫರ್​ಪುರದ ಅರ್ಪನಾ ದುಬೆ ಅಲಿಯಾಸ್​ ಮದನ್​ ಕುಮಾರ್ ಎಂಬ ವ್ಯಕ್ತಿಯನ್ನು ಗುಜರಾತ್ ಪೊಲೀಸರು ಬಂಧಿಸಿದ್ದಾರೆ. ಕುಮಾರ್ ಜನ್ಮ ದಿನಾಂಕ ಬದಲಾಯಿಸಿದ್ದು, ಐಪಿ ಅಡ್ರೆಸ್ ಮೂಲಕ ಆತನನ್ನು ಪತ್ತೆ ಮಾಡಲಾಗಿದೆ ಎಂದು ಮುಜಾಫರ್​ಪುರದ ಎಸ್‌ಎಸ್‌ಪಿ ರಾಕೇಶ್​ ಕುಮಾರ್ ತಿಳಿಸಿದ್ದಾರೆ.
author: 64a95e30e062050007777824

title: Lionel Messi consoles DJ Khaled's son after he cries ahead of match, video goes viral
content: Inter Miami captain Lionel Messi consoled DJ Khaled's seven-year-old son Asahd after he started crying ahead of Inter Miami's match against Atlanta United. Asahd had walked out on the pitch with Messi as a mascot. He started crying while standing in front of Messi, after which the Argentine footballer was seen consoling him.

title: इटली में जंगलों में लगी आग हाईवे तक पहुंची; आग से कुछ मीटर दूर से गुज़रती दिखीं कारें
content: इटली के सिसली रीजन में जंगलों में लगी आग हाईवे तक पहुंच गई है। ऑनलाइन सामने आए वीडियो में आग से कुछ मीटर की दूरी पर कार गुज़रती हुईं दिखाई दे रही हैं। आग लगने की घटना में सिसली में 3 लोगों की मौत हो गई है और सिसली के एक शहर में सोमवार को तापमान 47°C पहुंच गया।
author: 5f70e895d43821580e6d7098

title: Pics of Raghav Chadha being attacked by crow outside Parliament go viral
content: Pictures of a crow appearing to attack AAP Rajya Sabha MP Raghav Chadha outside the Parliament building amid the monsoon session went viral online. Chadha was seen ducking as the crow hovered over his head and pecked at him with its beak. Several Twitter users shared the pictures, with one saying, \This is a bad sign.\""
author: 5f70e896573ea2734e3862cc

title: Bill allowing multiple uses of birth certificate tabled in LS
content: A bill was introduced in Lok Sabha to allow use of birth certificate as single document for issuance of driving licence and admission to educational institutions. The Registration of Births and Deaths (Amendment) Bill will also allow birth certificate to be used as single document for preparation of voter list, Aadhaar number, registration of marriage and appointment to government jobs.
author: 5f70e896573ea2734e3862f5

title: Wildfire burns metres away from cars on highway in Italy, video surfaces
content: A video has surfaced on social media that showed wildfire burning a few metres away from cars being driven on a highway in Sicily, Italy. Italy’s southern island of Sicily has been witnessing wildfires that have killed three people. Fires in Sicily caused a temporary closure of Palermo airport after temperatures in the city climbed to 47°C on Monday.
author: 60086b83d438210f774299da

title: यूपी में सास और बहू ने एक-दूसरे को ज़मीन पर गिराकर की मारपीट व दी गालियां
content: अलीगढ़ (उत्तर प्रदेश) का एक वीडियो वायरल हो गया है जिसमें रानी देवी नामक महिला और उसकी बहू प्रीति देवी एक-दूसरे को ज़मीन पर गिराकर मारपीट करती और गालियां देती दिख रही हैं। रिपोर्ट्स के मुताबिक, यह वीडियो रानी के बेटे ने बनाया है। प्रीति ने आरोप लगाया कि बेटा न होने के कारण उसकी सास उसे ताना मारती है।
author: 619b85fa573ea266d0ebfee2

title: NASA shares video of Jupiter and its moon Io taken from JunoCam
content: NASA shared a video of Jupiter and its moon Io captured by the JunoCam. The Juno Spacecraft flew past the planet's volcanic moon Io, followed by the gas giant itself on May 16. Launched in 2011, Juno embarked on a journey to Jupiter to study its dense clouds and find answers to the origin and evolution of the planet.
author: 61cc1f6b573ea24b755b307a

title: US teen who ran away from home 4 years ago reaches police station
content: A 14-year-old who went missing from US' Phoenix nearly four years ago walked into Montana police station safely, officials said on Wednesday. She got her name removed from the missing children list. The girl, now 18, was described as autistic but high-functioning by her parents. She had left a note when she ran away from home stating, \I'll be back.\""
author: 61cc1f6b573ea24b755b307a

title: 2 teens stuck on bridge amid overflowing river in Rajasthan; had gone to shoot a video
content: A video has surfaced online which showed two teenagers being stuck on a bridge in Udaipur for over an hour after they tried to cross it on a bike as a nearby river overflowed. While the teenagers were rescued with the use of a hydraulic crane, as per officials of Civil Defence, they had gone there to shoot a video.
author: 60086b83d438210f774299da

title: Where does criticism go when you watch English films: Varun on 'Bawaal' Auschwitz scene
content: Speaking about the Auschwitz scene in his movie 'Bawaal', actor Varun Dhawan remarked why the same criticism isn’t applied to English films. In an indirect reference to the Bhagavad Gita scene in 'Oppenheimer’, Dhawan said, \They're allowed to do everything...I know people who’ve felt very triggered watching a small scene in a…recently released English film...Where does your criticism go then?\""
author: 60086b83d438210f774299da

title: Video captures moment woman gets swept away while crossing river in Telangana
content: A woman is still missing after she was swept away by the strong currents of the Kummaravagu River while trying to cross a flooded area in Telangana. A video of the incident showed a group of women trying to cross the region flooded due to incessant rainfall when a woman in green is dragged by the strong current.
author: 60086b83d438210f774299da

title: Video captures moment burning crane falls from 45 storeys in New York street
content: A construction crane partially smashed into a nearby building before collapsing in a street in New York. The crane was operating 45 storeys up when its engine compartment caught fire and injured at least six people. Several videos of the incident posted on social media showed the crane's arm carrying a 16-ton load of concrete before breaking off.
author: 60086b83d438210f774299da

title: 'What if same spoon is used for veg & non-veg,' says Sudha Murty; remark goes viral
content: Author Sudha Murty's remarks regarding her food preference have gone viral online. During an interview with 'Khaane Mein Kya Hai', Murty said, \I'm a pure vegetarian
newsType: I don't even eat eggs or garlic. What I am scared of is...what if the same spoon is used for both
author: vegetarian and non-vegetarian food...When we go out
categories: I only search for veg restaurants.\""

title: Khalid's bodyguard falls twice while running after singer in US, video surfaces
content: Singer-songwriter Khalid’s bodyguard fell twice while running after the singer as he waved to his fans after a performance in Nashville, US. A video of the incident showed the security official falling face-first twice as the singer ran backstage. In the video, Khalid seemed to have not noticed the fall and was gone by the second time the bodyguard fell.
author: 60086b83d438210f774299da

title: CCTV video shows moment speeding car hits biker, school students in K'taka
content: A hit-and-run case was caught on CCTV after a speeding car ran over three people in Karnataka’s Raichur. The video showed a biker taking a U-turn without noticing the car, following which the car hit him and two school students who were walking on the road. The car driver escaped from the spot soon after the incident occurred.
author: 60086b83d438210f774299da

title: Norway politician resigns after video of him stealing Hugo Boss sunglasses surfaces
content: Norwegian left-wing party leader Bjornar Moxnes resigned after he was caught on camera stealing a pair of Hugo Boss sunglasses from a duty-free outlet. After the video surfaced, Moxnes wrote on Facebook, \Many have asked how I could do something so stupid...I have not had a full explanation. I made a big mistake. I am very sorry.\""
author: 60086b83d438210f774299da

title: Republican leader Mitch McConnell freezes mid-sentence at press conference in US
content: Senate Republican Leader Mitch McConnell froze and stared into space midway through his opening remarks at a press conference in Capitol on Wednesday. A video of the incident showed his colleagues escorting him away from the cameras. Later, McConnell said he was feeling fine. In March, the 81-year-old suffered a concussion after falling at a Washington DC hotel.
author: 60086b83d438210f774299da

title: Cargo ship carrying 3,000 cars catches fire off Dutch coast, 1 Indian crew member dead
content: A cargo ship carrying 3,000 cars caught fire off the Dutch coast, killing one Indian crew member and injuring at least 20 others. Some of the crew members jumped off the ship’s deck into the sea in order to escape the fire. As per reports, the fire may have been started due to an electric vehicle on board the ship.
author: 60086b83d438210f774299da

title: What are 'Star Series' banknotes, over which RBI has issued a clarification?
content: RBI has clarified that banknotes with a star (*) symbol on the number panel are authentic. The symbol is an identifier indicating that the note is a replacement for defectively printed ones in a packet of 100 pieces of serially numbered banknotes. They are exactly similar to the other banknotes, but have an additional character, which is the *(star).
author: 5f70e895573ea2734e386297

title: Unaware: Cipla on 'promoters to sell stake' reports
content: Cipla on Thursday responded to media reports claiming the firm's promoters were planning to sell a part of their 33.47% stake in the pharma major. \We hereby clarify that the company isn't aware of any event that requires disclosure under Listing Regulations
newsType: \" Cipla said. \"The company will make appropriate disclosure...as and when any such requirement arises
author: \" it added."

title: Adani lenders consider up to $750 mn loan for Ambuja debt: Report
content: Barclays, Deutsche Bank and Standard Chartered are in talks with Adani Group to lend between $600 million and $750 million collectively to refinance the debt taken to fund its purchase of Ambuja Cements, Bloomberg reported citing sources. The loan would be syndicated, the report said. The talks haven't yet concluded and the amounts could still change.
author: 62dabeebd438213aabd919fa

title: Tata Motors' shares rise 3%, hit 52-week high day after Q1 result
content: Tata Motors' shares rose over 3% to hit a new 52-week high of ₹665.3/piece on BSE in early trade, a day after it reported a consolidated net profit of ₹3,203 crore for the quarter ended June. The rise was boosted by the improved margin of its passenger vehicle business and robust sales at its Jaguar Land Rover unit.
author: 62dabeebd438213aabd919fa

title: AI can't be allowed to be used for hurting mankind: Samsung's Park
content: Samsung's South West Asia CEO JB Park said the prospect of self-learning artificial intelligence would unfold unprecedented opportunities in the digital age. When asked about fears of AI systems becoming self-aware, he cautioned that AI cannot be allowed to be used for hurting mankind. He also spoke on the need to be careful in deploying AI in the defence industry.
author: 62dabeebd438213aabd919fa

title: Tata Motors' shares rise 3%, hit 52-week high day after Q1 result
content: Tata Motors' shares rose over 3% to hit a new 52-week high of ₹665.3/piece on BSE in early trade on Wednesday, a day after it reported a consolidated net profit of ₹3,203 crore for the quarter ended June. The rise was boosted by the improved margin of its passenger vehicle business and robust sales at its Jaguar Land Rover unit.
author: 62dabeebd438213aabd919fa

title: ಮಳೆಗೆ ಜೀವ ಹಾಗೂ ಬೆಳೆ ಹಾನಿಯಾಗದಂತೆ ಮುಂಜಾಗ್ರತೆ ವಹಿಸಲು ಮೈಸೂರು ಜಿಲ್ಲಾಧಿಕಾರಿ ಸೂಚನೆ
content: ಹೆಚ್ಚಾಗುತ್ತಿರುವ ಮಳೆಯಿಂದ ಮೈಸೂರಿನಲ್ಲಿ ಜೀವ ಹಾಗೂ ಬೆಳೆ ಹಾನಿ ಉಂಟಾಗದಂತೆ ಕ್ರಮ ಕೈಗೊಳ್ಳಲು ಜಿಲ್ಲಾಧಿಕಾರಿ ಡಾ. ಕೆ.ವಿ. ರಾಜೇಂದ್ರ ಸೂಚಿಸಿದ್ದಾರೆ. ತಾಲ್ಲೂಕು ಮಟ್ಟದ ಅಧಿಕಾರಿಗಳ ಜತೆ ಗುರುವಾರ ಸಭೆ ನಡೆಸಿದ ಅವರು, ಪರಿಹಾರ ಕೇಂದ್ರ ಸ್ಥಾಪಿಸಿ ತಗ್ಗು ಪ್ರದೇಶದ ಜನರಿಗೆ ನಿರಂತರ ಎಚ್ಚರಿಕೆ ನೀಡುತ್ತಿರಬೇಕು. ಸರ್ಕಾರಿ ಶಾಲೆ ಮತ್ತು ಅಂಗನವಾಡಿ ಕಟ್ಟಡಗಳ ದುರಸ್ತಿ ಮಾಡಬೇಕು ಎಂದು ಹೇಳಿದ್ದಾರೆ. ಶಾಲೆಗಳಿಗೆ ರಜೆ ಘೋಷಿಸುವ ಮುನ್ನ ಪರಿಸ್ಥಿತಿ ಅವಲೋಕಿಸಲು ಸೂಚಿಸಿದ್ದಾರೆ.
author: 64a5146bc53ce0000790f33a

title: ಸೌಜನ್ಯ ಪ್ರಕರಣದಲ್ಲಿ ದೂರು ಮರು ದಾಖಲಿಸಿ ತನಿಖೆ ನಡೆಸಲು ಸಿಎಂಗೆ ಮೈಸೂರಿನ ಒಡನಾಡಿ ಸಂಸ್ಥೆ ಪತ್ರ
content: 2012ರಲ್ಲಿ ಧರ್ಮಸ್ಥಳ ಭಾಗದಲ್ಲಿ ನಡೆದ ಸೌಜನ್ಯ ಅಪಹರಣ ಹಾಗೂ ಅತ್ಯಾಚಾರ ಪ್ರಕರಣವನ್ನು ಪೋಷಕರ ದೂರಿನ ಅನ್ವಯ ಮರು ದಾಖಲಿಸಿಕೊಂಡು, ನಿವೃತ್ತ ನ್ಯಾಯಾಧೀಶರ ನಿರ್ದೇಶನದಲ್ಲಿ ಸೂಕ್ತ ತನಿಖೆ ನಡೆಸಿ ನ್ಯಾಯ ಒದಗಿಸಬೇಕು ಎಂದು ಕೋರಿ ಮೈಸೂರಿನ ಒಡನಾಡಿ ಸೇವಾಸಂಸ್ಥೆ ಸಿಎಂ ಹಾಗೂ ಗೃಹಸಚಿವರಿಗೆ ಬುಧವಾರ ಪತ್ರ ಬರೆದಿದೆ. ವಿನಾಕಾರಣ ಆರೋಪಿಯಾಗಿ ದೈಹಿಕ, ಮಾನಸಿಕ ಕ್ಷೋಭೆಗೆ ಒಳಗಾಗಿ ಆರು ವರ್ಷ ಜೈಲುಶಿಕ್ಷೆ ಅನುಭವಿಸಿದ ಸಂತೋಷ್ ರಾವ್‌ಗೆ ಪರಿಹಾರ ನೀಡಬೇಕೆಂದು ಪತ್ರದಲ್ಲಿ ಉಲ್ಲೇಖಿಸಲಾಗಿದೆ.
author: 64a51b9a095ebc00070d3cde

title: ಉಡುಪಿಯ ಕಾಲೇಜು ಶೌಚಾಲಯದಲ್ಲಿ ವಿಡಿಯೋ ಶೂಟ್, ಮೂವರು ವಿದ್ಯಾರ್ಥಿನಿಯರ ವಿರುದ್ಧ ಪ್ರಕರಣ ದಾಖಲು
content: ಉಡುಪಿಯ ನೇತ್ರಜ್ಯೋತಿ ಪ್ಯಾರಾ ಮೆಡಿಕಲ್ ಕಾಲೇಜಿನ ಶೌಚಾಲಯದಲ್ಲಿ ವಿದ್ಯಾರ್ಥಿನಿಯ ವಿಡಿಯೋ ಚಿತ್ರೀಕರಿಸಿದ ಕಾಲೇಜಿನ ವಿದ್ಯಾರ್ಥಿನಿಯರಾದ ಶಬನಾಝ್, ಅಲ್ಫೀಯಾ, ಅಲಿಮಾ ವಿರುದ್ಧ ಮಲ್ಪೆ ಠಾಣೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ಸ್ವಯಂಪ್ರೇರಿತ ಪ್ರಕರಣ ದಾಖಲಾಗಿದೆ. ಮಹಿಳೆಯ ಮಾನ ಮತ್ತು ಗೌರವಕ್ಕೆ ಧಕ್ಕೆ, ಮಹಿಳೆಯ ಖಾಸಗಿತನವನ್ನು ಮೊಬೈಲ್‌ನಲ್ಲಿ ಚಿತ್ರೀಕರಣ ಮಾಡಿದ ಆರೋಪದ ಮೇಲೆ ವಿದ್ಯಾರ್ಥಿನಿಯರು ಹಾಗೂ ನೇತ್ರಜ್ಯೋತಿ ಕಾಲೇಜಿನ ಆಡಳಿತ ಮಂಡಳಿ ವಿರುದ್ಧವೂ ಪ್ರಕರಣ ದಾಖಲಾಗಿದೆ.
author: 64a51be0095ebc00070d3d33

title: ಮೈಸೂರು ಮಹಾನಗರ ಪಾಲಿಕೆ ಆಯುಕ್ತರಾಗಿ ಅಸಾದ್ ಉರ್ ರೆಹಮಾನ್ ಶರೀಫ್ ಅಧಿಕಾರ ಸ್ವೀಕಾರ
content: ಮೈಸೂರು ಮಹಾನಗರ ಪಾಲಿಕೆ ಆಯುಕ್ತರಾಗಿ ಅಸಾದ್ ಉರ್ ರೆಹಮಾನ್ ಶರೀಫ್ ಅವರು ಗುರುವಾರ ಅಧಿಕಾರ ಸ್ವೀಕರಿಸಿದರು. ಈವರೆಗೆ ಆಯುಕ್ತರಾಗಿದ್ದ ಜಿ. ಲಕ್ಷ್ಮೀಕಾಂತ ರೆಡ್ಡಿ ಅವರನ್ನು ವರ್ಗಾವಣೆ ಮಾಡಿರುವ ಸರ್ಕಾರ, ಈ ಸ್ಥಾನಕ್ಕೆ ಕೆಎಂಎಎಸ್‌ನ ಗ್ರೇಡ್-1 ಅಧಿಕಾರಿ ಅಸಾದ್ ಉರ್ ರೆಹಮಾನ್ ಶರೀಫ್ ಅವರನ್ನು ನೇಮಿಸಿದೆ. ಇದೇ ವೇಳೆ ಮಾತನಾಡಿದ ಅವರು, ನಗರದ ಸ್ವಚ್ಛತೆ, ಆರೋಗ್ಯ ಮತ್ತು ಮೂಲ ಸೌಲಭ್ಯಕ್ಕೆ ಹೆಚ್ಚು ಗಮನ ಹರಿಸುತ್ತೇನೆ ಎಂದು ತಿಳಿಸಿದರು.
author: 64a51be0095ebc00070d3d33

title: ಮೈಸೂರಿನಲ್ಲಿ ಕಾರ್ಖಾನೆ ಸ್ಥಗಿತ, ಕಾರ್ಮಿಕರಿಗೆ ಪರಿಹಾರ ನೀಡುವಂತೆ ನ್ಯಾಯಾಲಯ ಆದೇಶ
content: ಕಾರ್ಖಾನೆ ಬಂದ್ ಆಗಿದ್ದರಿಂದ ಕೆಲಸ ಕಳೆದುಕೊಂಡಿದ್ದ 300ಕ್ಕೂ ಹೆಚ್ಚು ಕಾರ್ಮಿಕರಿಗೆ ಪರಿಹಾರ ನೀಡುವಂತೆ ಎಂ.ಕೆ.ಫ್ಯಾಶನ್ ವರ್ಲ್ಡ್ ಕಂಪನಿಗೆ ಮೈಸೂರು ಕಾರ್ಮಿಕ ನ್ಯಾಯಾಲಯ ಆದೇಶಿಸಿದೆ. ಈ ಬಗ್ಗೆ ಮಂಗಳವಾರ ಮಾತನಾಡಿದ ಜಿಲ್ಲಾ ಗಾರ್ಮೆಂಟ್ಸ್ ಕಾರ್ಮಿಕರ ಸಂಘದ ಅಧ್ಯಕ್ಷ ಪ್ರಮೋದ್ ಚಿಕ್ಕಮಣ್ಣೂರು “ಕಾರ್ಮಿಕರಿಗೆ ತಲಾ ₹2.50 ಲಕ್ಷ ಪರಿಹಾರ ನೀಡುವಂತೆ ಮೇ 24ರಂದು ನ್ಯಾಯಾಲಯ ಆದೇಶಿಸಿದೆ. ಇಂದಿಗೂ ಪರಿಹಾರದ ಹಣ ದೊರೆತಿಲ್ಲ. ಶೀಘ್ರವೇ ಕಾನೂನು ಕ್ರಮಕ್ಕೆ ಮುಂದಾಗಲಿದ್ದೇವೆ” ಎಂದರು.
author: 64a51be0095ebc00070d3d33

title: ಕೇಂದ್ರ ಕಾರಾಗೃಹದಲ್ಲಿರುವ ನಜೀರ್‌ನನ್ನು ನ್ಯಾಯಾಲಯಕ್ಕೆ ಕರೆತರಲು ಸಿಸಿಬಿಗೆ ಅನುಮತಿ: ವರದಿ
content: ಬೆಂಗಳೂರಿನಲ್ಲಿ ಸ್ಫೋಟಕ್ಕೆ ಸಂಚು ರೂಪಿಸಿದ್ದ ಪ್ರಕರಣದ ಆರೋಪಿ, ಪರಪ್ಪನ ಅಗ್ರಹಾರ ಕೇಂದ್ರ ಕಾರಾಗೃಹದಲ್ಲಿರುವ ನಜೀರ್‌ನನ್ನು ನ್ಯಾಯಾಲಯಕ್ಕೆ ಹಾಜರು ಪಡಿಸಲು ಸಿಸಿಬಿಗೆ ಅನುಮತಿ ಸಿಕ್ಕಿದೆ ಎಂದು ವರದಿಗಳು ಹೇಳಿವೆ. 2008ರ ಸರಣಿ ಬಾಂಬ್ ಸ್ಫೋಟದ ಆರೋಪಿ ನಜೀರ್,‌ ಶಂಕಿತ ಉಗ್ರರಿಗೆ ಜೈಲಿನಲ್ಲಿ ಸ್ಫೋಟಕ್ಕೆ ತರಬೇತಿ ನೀಡುತ್ತಿದ್ದ ಎಂದು ತನಿಖೆಯಿಂದ ಗೊತ್ತಾಗಿದೆ. ಗುರುವಾರ ನ್ಯಾಯಾಧೀಶರ ಎದುರು ಹಾಜರು ಪಡಿಸಿ, ಸಿಸಿಬಿ ವಶಕ್ಕೆ ನೀಡುವಂತೆ ಕೋರಲಾಗುವುದು ಎಂದು ವರದಿಗಳು ತಿಳಿಸಿವೆ.
author: 64a51be0095ebc00070d3d33

title: ಮೆಟ್ರೋ ಪಿಲ್ಲರ್ ಕುಸಿದು ಇಬ್ಬರು ಮೃತಪಟ್ಟ ಪ್ರಕರಣ, ಸರ್ಕಾರಕ್ಕೆ ಹೈಕೋರ್ಟ್ ನೋಟಿಸ್
content: ಬೆಂಗಳೂರಿನಲ್ಲಿ ನಿರ್ಮಾಣ ಹಂತದ ಮೆಟ್ರೋ ಪಿಲ್ಲರ್ ಕುಸಿದು ಮಹಿಳೆ ಹಾಗೂ ಆಕೆಯ ಪುತ್ರನ ಸಾವು ಪ್ರಕರಣ ಹಿನ್ನೆಲೆ ₹10 ಕೋಟಿ ಪರಿಹಾರ ಕೋರಿ ಮೃತಳ ಪತಿ ಸಲ್ಲಿಸಿದ ಅರ್ಜಿ ಸಂಬಂಧ ಸರ್ಕಾರ ಹಾಗೂ ಬಿಎಂಆರ್‌ಸಿಎಲ್‌ಗೆ ನೋಟಿಸ್ ನೀಡಲು ಹೈಕೋರ್ಟ್ ಆದೇಶಿಸಿದೆ. ಮಂಗಳವಾರ ಮೃತಳ ಪತಿ ಲೋಹಿತ್ ಕುಮಾರ್ ಸಲ್ಲಿಸಿದ ರಿಟ್ ಅರ್ಜಿ ವಿಚಾರಣೆ ನಡೆಸಿದ ಹೈಕೋರ್ಟ್, ರಾಜ್ಯ ಸರ್ಕಾರ ಹಾಗೂ ಬಿಎಂಆರ್​ಸಿಎಲ್​ ಸೇರಿ 8 ಪ್ರತಿವಾದಿಗಳಿಗೆ ನೋಟಿಸ್ ಜಾರಿಗೊಳಿಸಲು ಆದೇಸಿದ್ದು, 2 ವಾರ ವಿಚಾರಣೆ ಮುಂದೂಡಿದೆ.
author: 64a95e30e062050007777824

title: ರವಿ ಪೂಜಾರಿ ಪ್ರಕರಣದಲ್ಲಿ ಸ್ಪಷ್ಟನೆ ಕೇಳಿ ಕೇಂದ್ರಕ್ಕೆ ಕರ್ನಾಟಕ ಹೈಕೋರ್ಟ್ ನೋಟಿಸ್
content: ರವಿ ಪೂಜಾರಿ ಪ್ರಕರಣದ ಹಸ್ತಾಂತರ ಆದೇಶದಲ್ಲಿ ಉಲ್ಲೇಖಿಸದೇ ಇರುವ ಪ್ರಕರಣಗಳ ವಿಚಾರಣೆ ನಡೆಸಬಹುದೆ ಎಂದು ಸ್ಪಷ್ಟನೆ ನೀಡುವಂತೆ ಕೇಂದ್ರ ಸರ್ಕಾರಕ್ಕೆ ಬುಧವಾರ ಕರ್ನಾಟಕ ಹೈಕೋರ್ಟ್ ನೋಟಿಸ್‌ ನೀಡಿದೆ. ಸೆನೆಗಲ್‌ನಿಂದ ಹಸ್ತಾಂತರಿಸುವ ವೇಳೆ ಉಲ್ಲೇಖಿಸಿರುವ ಪ್ರಕರಣಗಳಡಿ ಮಾತ್ರ ನನ್ನ ವಿಚಾರಣೆ ನಡೆಸಬೇಕೆಂದು ಕೋರಿ ಹೈರ್ಕೋರ್ಟ್‌ಗೆ ರವಿ ಪೂಜಾರಿ ಅರ್ಜಿ ಸಲ್ಲಿಸಿದ್ದರು. ವಿಚಾರಣೆ ನಡೆಸಿದ ಹೈಕೋರ್ಟ್, ಸ್ಪಷ್ಟನೆ ನೀಡುವಂತೆ ಕೇಂದ್ರಕ್ಕೆ ನೋಟಿಸ್ ಜಾರಿ ಮಾಡಿ ವಿಚಾರಣೆ ಮುಂದೂಡಿದೆ.
author: 64a95e30e062050007777824

title: ಕರ್ನಾಟಕದಲ್ಲಿ 8.07 ಲಕ್ಷ ನರೇಗಾ ಕಾರ್ಮಿಕರ ಜಾಬ್ ಕಾರ್ಡ್ ರದ್ದು
content: ಕರ್ನಾಟಕದಲ್ಲಿ 2022-23ರಲ್ಲಿ  8.07 ಲಕ್ಷ ನರೇಗಾ ಕಾರ್ಮಿಕರ ಜಾಬ್ ಕಾರ್ಡ್ ರದ್ದುಗೊಳಿಸಲಾಗಿದೆ ಎಂದು ಮಂಗಳವಾರ ಲೋಕಸಭೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ಕೇಂದ್ರ ಪಂಚಾಯತ್‌ರಾಜ್ ಸಚಿವ ಗಿರಿರಾಜ್ ಸಿಂಗ್ ತಿಳಿಸಿದರು. “ಇಲಾಖೆಯು ಕರ್ನಾಟಕಕ್ಕೆ 2022-23ರಲ್ಲಿ ₹8,107 ಕೋಟಿ ಅನುದಾನ ನೀಡಿದ್ದು, ಯಾವುದೇ ನರೇಗಾ ಕಾರ್ಮಿಕರ ಕೂಲಿಯನ್ನು ಬಾಕಿ ಉಳಿಸಿಕೊಂಡಿಲ್ಲ. ಈ ವರ್ಷದ ಜುಲೈ 21ರ ವರೆಗೆ ಕೂಲಿ ಸಾಮಗ್ರಿಗಳ ಬಾಕಿ ₹579 ಕೋಟಿ ಇದೆ” ಎಂದು ಸಚಿವರು ಮಾಹಿತಿ ನೀಡಿದ್ದಾರೆ.
author: 64a95e30e062050007777824

title: ಕರ್ನಾಟಕದ 2ನೇ ಅಧಿಕೃತ ಭಾಷೆಗೆ ತುಳು ಅರ್ಹ, ರಾಜ್ಯ ಸರ್ಕಾರಕ್ಕೆ ಶಿಫಾರಸು
content: ತುಳು ಭಾಷೆ ರಾಜ್ಯದ 2ನೇ ಅಧಿಕೃತ ಭಾಷೆ ಎಂದು ಘೋಷಿಸಲು ಅರ್ಹ ಎಂದು ಡಾ. ಎಂ.ಮೋಹನ್ ಆಳ್ವ ನೇತೃತ್ವದ ಸಮಿತಿ ರಾಜ್ಯ ಸರ್ಕಾರಕ್ಕೆ ಶಿಫಾರಸು ಮಾಡಿದೆ ಎಂದು ಪ್ರಜಾವಾಣಿ ವರದಿ ಮಾಡಿದೆ. ತಮಿಳು-ಕನ್ನಡ ಭಾಷೆಗಳಷ್ಟೆ ಪ್ರಾಚೀನವಾದ ತುಳು ಭಾಷೆ, ಶೈಕ್ಷಣಿಕವಾಗಿ, ಸಾಂಸ್ಕೃತಿಕವಾಗಿ ಬೆಳವಣಿಗೆ ಹೊಂದಿದೆ ಎಂದು ಸಮಿತಿ ಹೇಳಿದೆ. ತುಳು ಭಾಷೆಯನ್ನು ರಾಜ್ಯದ 2ನೇ ಅಧಿಕೃತ ಭಾಷೆಯಾಗಿ ಘೋಷಿಸುವ ಕುರಿತು ಅಧ್ಯಯನ ನಡೆಸಿ ವರದಿ ಸಲ್ಲಿಸಲು ಈ ಹಿಂದಿನ ಬಿಜೆಪಿ ಸರ್ಕಾರ ಸಮಿತಿ ರಚಿಸಿತ್ತು.
author: 64a95e30e062050007777824

title: ಕರ್ನಾಟಕದ ಖಾಸಗಿ ವೈದ್ಯಕೀಯ ಕಾಲೇಜುಗಳ ಶುಲ್ಕ ಶೇ.10ರಷ್ಟು ಹೆಚ್ಚಳ
content: ರಾಜ್ಯದ ಖಾಸಗಿ ವೈದ್ಯಕೀಯ ಕಾಲೇಜುಗಳು ಪ್ರಸಕ್ತ ವರ್ಷದಿಂದಲೇ ಶೇ.10ರಷ್ಟು ಶುಲ್ಕ ಹೆಚ್ಚಳ ಮಾಡಲು ವೈದ್ಯಕೀಯ ಶಿಕ್ಷಣ ಇಲಾಖೆ ಸಮ್ಮತಿಸಿದೆ. “2022-23ನೇ ಶೈಕ್ಷಣಿಕ ವರ್ಷದಲ್ಲಿ ಅಲ್ಪ ಸಂಖ್ಯಾತರ ಒಡೆತನದ ವೈದ್ಯಕೀಯ ಕಾಲೇಜುಗಳಲ್ಲಿ ಶುಲ್ಕ ಹೆಚ್ಚಿಸಲಾಗಿತ್ತು. ಆದ್ದರಿಂದ ಈ ವರ್ಷ ಅಲ್ಪ ಸಂಖ್ಯಾತರ ಕಾಲೇಜುಗಳನ್ನು ಹೊರತುಪಡಿಸಿ ಉಳಿದ ಖಾಸಗಿ ಕಾಲೇಜುಗಳಿಗೆ ಶುಲ್ಕ ಹೆಚ್ಚಿಸಲು ಅನುಮತಿಸಲಾಗಿದೆ” ಎಂದು ವೈದ್ಯಕೀಯ ಶಿಕ್ಷಣ ಸಚಿವ ಶರಣ ಪ್ರಕಾಶ ಪಾಟೀಲ್ ಹೇಳಿದರು.
author: 64a95e30e062050007777824

title: एमएस धोनी के 2012 के जॉब अपॉइंटमेंट लेटर की तस्वीर हुई वायरल
content: पूर्व भारतीय कप्तान एमएस धोनी के 2012 के जॉब अपॉइंटमेंट लेटर की तस्वीर सोशल मीडिया पर वायरल हो गई है। अपॉइंटमेंट लेटर के अनुसार, धोनी को ₹43,000 बेसिक पे, ₹21,970 महंगाई भत्ता और ₹60,000 विशेष भत्ता के साथ इंडिया सीमेंट्स का वाइस प्रेसिडेंट (मार्केंटिंग) नियुक्त किया गया था। एक फैन ने कमेंट किया, \बेसिक पे से अधिक विशेष भत्ता है।\""
author: 5f70e894d43821580e6d7032

title: दुनियाभर में स्कूलों में स्मार्टफोन पर लगाया जाए प्रतिबंध: यूएन
content: संयुक्त राष्ट्र शैक्षिक, वैज्ञानिक एवं सांस्कृतिक संगठन (यूनेस्को) ने दुनियाभर के स्कूलों में स्मार्टफोन पर प्रतिबंध की अनुशंसा की है। यूनेस्को की एक रिपोर्ट के मुताबिक, इस बात के सबूत हैं कि फोन के अत्यधिक इस्तेमाल का संबंध शैक्षणिक प्रदर्शन में गिरावट से जुड़ा है। यूनेस्को ने बताया कि टेक्नोलॉजी का इस्तेमाल लर्निंग एक्सपीरियंस बेहतर बनाने के लिए होना चाहिए।
author: 5f70e895d43821580e6d7098

title: Ban smartphones in schools worldwide, says UN
content: The United Nations Educational, Scientific and Cultural Organization (UNESCO) recommended a ban on smartphones in schools worldwide. A UNESCO report said there was proof that excessive use of mobile phones is linked to reduced educational performance. Technology's use \must be for enhanced learning experiences and for the wellbeing of students and teachers
author: UNESCO said."

title: Lawrence Bishnoi’s aide Vikram Brar arrested from UAE in Sidhu Moosewala's murder
content: A team of NIA went to Dubai to arrest an aide of jailed gangster Lawrence Bishnoi in connection to singer Sidhu Moosewala's murder. Vikramjeet Singh alias Vikram Brar, who was absconding since 2020, was arrested after his deportation from the UAE. Brar was also involved in the killings of businessmen, smuggling of weapons, and extortion in India, NIA said.
author: 5f70e896573ea2734e3862cc

title: Patient attacks doctor with knife at Delhi's Ganga Ram Hospital, video surfaces
content: A senior doctor at the Sir Ganga Ram Hospital in Delhi was attacked with a knife by a patient during a consultation session on Wednesday. The 21-year-old patient was undergoing treatment for depression at the hospital since 2021. The hospital security and an attendant of the doctor intervened and the man was handed over to the police.
author: 60086b59573ea2797ef6df10

title: Punjabi singer Surinder Shinda passes away aged 64
content: Punjabi singer Surinder Shinda passed away at the age of 64 on Wednesday. He was not keeping well and was hospitalised in Ludhiana for over 20 days. Shinda has several hit songs including 'Jatt Jeona Morh', 'Putt Jattan De', 'Truck Billiya', 'Balbiro Bhabhi,' and 'Kaher Singh Di Mout'.
author: 60086b59573ea2797ef6df10

title: CCTV video shows moment speeding car hits biker, school students in K'taka
content: A hit-and-run case was caught on CCTV after a speeding car ran over three people in Karnataka’s Raichur. The video showed a biker taking a U-turn without noticing the car, following which the car hit him and two school students who were walking on the road. The car driver escaped from the spot soon after the incident occurred.
author: 60086b83d438210f774299da

title: Khalid's bodyguard falls twice while running after singer in US, video surfaces
content: Singer-songwriter Khalid’s bodyguard fell twice while running after the singer as he waved to his fans after a performance in Nashville, US. A video of the incident showed the security official falling face-first twice as the singer ran backstage. In the video, Khalid seemed to have not noticed the fall and was gone by the second time the bodyguard fell.
author: 60086b83d438210f774299da

title: Couple sells 8-month-old son to buy iPhone for making Instagram Reels in West Bengal
content: A couple from West Bengal allegedly sold their eight-month-old son to buy an iPhone and make Instagram Reels. They travelled to various parts of West Bengal to shoot videos, claimed reports. A local councillor Tarak Guha said the husband, Jaydev, was arrested after their neighbours informed the police. He alleged that Jaydev also tried selling his seven-year-old daughter.
author: 60ae2b15573ea27d7e496a9f

title: Wife's inability to bear child no ground for divorce: Patna High Court
content: The Patna High Court recently commented that a wife's inability to bear a child is neither impotence nor any ground for divorce under Hindu Marriage Act while dismissing a man's petition challenging a lower court's order rejecting his divorce plea. The court said couples may opt for adoption. The petitioner had claimed his wife didn't want to consummate the marriage.
author: 60ae2b15573ea27d7e496a9f

title: I agree: Vaas on MSD's remark over formats Pathirana should play
content: Reacting to MS Dhoni's earlier statement where he'd said that Sri Lankan pacer Matheesha Pathirana shouldn't even get close to red-ball cricket and focus on ICC tournaments, ex-Sri Lanka pacer Chaminda Vaas said, \I agree.\" \"When...time comes
author: \" he added. \"Even in white-ball cricket

title: भारतीय फुटबॉल टीमों को मिली एशियन गेम्स में हिस्सा लेने की अनुमति
content: भारतीय पुरुष और महिला फुटबॉल टीमों को एशियन गेम्स में हिस्सा लेने की अनुमति मिल गई है। दरअसल, किसी टूर्नामेंट में दोनों टीमों के हिस्सा लेने के नियमों में सरकार द्वारा बदलाव करने के बाद ऐसा हुआ है। खेल मंत्री अनुराग ठाकुर ने कहा, \हाल के दिनों में दोनों टीमों के प्रदर्शन को देखते हुए...यह छूट दी गई है।\""
author: 62bec075573ea25553962618

title: क्या हैं 'स्टार सीरीज़' वाले बैंक नोट जिनको लेकर आरबीआई ने जारी किया स्पष्टीकरण?
content: आरबीआई ने स्पष्ट किया है कि वैसे नोट भी वैध हैं जिनके नंबर पैनल पर स्टार (*) अंकित है। बकौल आरबीआई, यह निशान इस बात की पहचान करता है कि नोट बदला गया है या फिर नोट के खराब हो जाने के बाद उसी नंबर से दोबारा छापा गया है। कुछ सोशल मीडिया यूज़र्स ने इन्हें फर्ज़ी बताया था।
author: 62bec075573ea25553962618

title: પંજાબી ગાયક સુરિન્દર શિંદાનું 64 વર્ષની વયે નિધન
content: પંજાબી ગાયક સુરિન્દર શિંદાનું બુધવારે 64 વર્ષની વયે નિધન થયું છે. તેમની તબિયત સારી ન હતી અને 20 દિવસથી વધુ સમયથી લુધિયાણાની હોસ્પિટલમાં દાખલ હતા. શિંદાએ 'જટ્ટ જીઓના મોર', 'પુટ જટ્ટન દે', 'ટ્રક બિલિયા', 'બલબીરો ભાભી' અને 'કેહર સિંહ દી મૌત' સહિતના ઘણા હિટ ગીતો આપ્યા છે.
author: 64a11524e1142b00074d12be

title: 64 ವರ್ಷದ ಪಂಜಾಬಿ ಗಾಯಕ ಸುರಿಂದರ್ ಶಿಂದಾ ನಿಧನ
content: ಪಂಜಾಬಿ ಗಾಯಕ ಸುರಿಂದರ್ ಶಿಂದಾ ಅವರು ಬುಧವಾರ 64 ನೇ ವಯಸ್ಸಿನಲ್ಲಿ ನಿಧನರಾದರು. ಅನಾರೋಗ್ಯದಿಂದಾಗಿ ಕಳೆದ 20 ದಿನಗಳಿಂದ ಲುಧಿಯಾನದ ಆಸ್ಪತ್ರೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ಚಿಕಿತ್ಸೆ ಪಡೆಯುತ್ತಿದ್ದ ಅವರು, ಇಂದು ಬೆಳಿಗ್ಗೆ ಕೊನೆಯುಸಿರೆಳೆದಿದ್ದಾರೆ.  ಸುರಿಂದರ್ ಶಿಂದಾ ಅವರು 'ಜಟ್ಟ್ ಜಿಯೋನಾ ಮೋರ್ಹ್', 'ಪುಟ್ ಜತ್ತನ್ ದೇ', 'ಟ್ರಕ್ ಬಿಲ್ಲಿಯಾ', 'ಬಲ್ಬಿರೋ ಭಾಭಿ,' ಮತ್ತು 'ಕಹೇರ್ ಸಿಂಗ್ ದಿ ಮೌತ್' ಸೇರಿದಂತೆ ಹಲವಾರು ಹಿಟ್ ಹಾಡುಗಳನ್ನು ನೀಡಿದ್ದಾರೆ.
author: 64a11562d7301500079ed581

title: Expect changes in ODI World Cup 2023 schedule: BCCI Secretary Jay Shah
content: BCCI Secretary Jay Shah has said that the BCCI has received proposals from two to three member boards to shift the dates of some ODI World Cup 2023 matches. He stated that changes in the schedule are expected, adding that it's not specific to India-Pakistan match. He further said that venues won't be changed.
author: 5f70de9bd43821580e6d7022

title: Suryakumar dons Samson's jersey in ODI, fans react as pic goes viral
content: Team India batter Suryakumar Yadav was seen wearing Sanju Samson's jersey in the first ODI against West Indies. After the picture went viral, a fan jokingly tweeted, \Took his place as well as his jersey.\" Another wrote
newsType: \"Beautiful friendship.\" \"At least his jersey made it to the playing XI
author: \" a fan sarcastically tweeted."

title: Video of Virat Kohli's one-handed diving catch at slips goes viral
content: A video has gone viral showing former Team India captain Virat Kohli pulling off a one-handed catch at second slip during the first ODI against West Indies in Barbados. Kohli took the catch on Ravindra Jadeja's bowling to dismiss Romario Shepherd for a duck. Kohli had moved to the second slip just before the ball on which Shepherd got out.
author: 5f70de9bd43821580e6d7022

title: Team India jersey for ODI series against West Indies unveiled, fans troll BCCI
content: BCCI unveiled the India jersey for the upcoming ODI series against West Indies. Several fans trolled the BCCI over the sponsor logo in front of the jersey, with a fan tweeting, \That Dream11 logo bigger than India is hurting my eyes.\" Another wrote
author: Dream11 is our country and India is the main sponsor.\""

title: Bumrah's short run-up, walks & jumps to bowl, is potent: Ambrose
content: Talking about India pacer Jasprit Bumrah, ex-West Indies pacer Curtly Ambrose said Bumrah is not a \conventional fast bowler with a long run-up\". \"He has...short run-up
author: takes two or three strides and jumps to deliver
categories: \" Ambrose stated. He added that Bumrah is different but \"highly effective\". Bumrah has taken 128 wickets in 30 Tests so far."

title: Replacing Rishabh Pant big ask but Kishan can score briskly: Karim
content: Talking about India wicketkeeper-batter Ishan Kishan, ex-India cricketer Saba Karim said replacing Rishabh Pant is a \big ask\" but Kishan can score runs briskly. \"Kishan has delivered on both fronts [batting and wicketkeeping]
newsType: showing remarkable progress in his skills
author: \" Karim stated. Kishan scored 52* off 34 balls in India's second innings in second Test against West Indies."

title: वेस्टइंडीज़ के खिलाफ मैच में सैमसन की जर्सी पहने दिखे सूर्यकुमार यादव, वायरल हुई तस्वीर
content: वेस्टइंडीज़ के खिलाफ पहले वनडे के दौरान भारतीय बल्लेबाज़ सूर्यकुमार यादव ने संजू सैमसन की जर्सी पहनी जिसकी तस्वीर वायरल हो गई है। तस्वीर पर एक ट्विटर यूज़र ने मज़ाक में लिखा, \सूर्यकुमार ने सैमसन की जगह के साथ-साथ उनकी जर्सी भी ले ली।\" वहीं
author: \"कम-से-कम उनकी (सैमसन) जर्सी को तो प्लेइंग इलेवन में जगह मिली।\""

title: భద్రాచలం వద్ద 48 అడుగులకు చేరిన గోదావరి నీటిమట్టం, రెండో ప్రమాద హెచ్చరిక జారీ
content: ఎడతెరిపిలేని వర్షాలతో భద్రాచలం వద్ద బుధవారం రాత్రి 9.28 గంటలకు గోదావరి నీటిమట్టం 48 అడుగులకు చేరింది. దీంతో రెండో ప్రమాద హెచ్చరిక జారీ చేసినట్లు కలెక్టర్‌ ప్రియాంక అల తెలిపారు. ఇప్పటికే రామాలయం చుట్టూ నీరు చేరింది. ఇవాళ మధ్యాహ్నం 3 గంటల వరకు 44.4 అడుగుల మేర నీటిమట్టం చేరడంతో మొదటి ప్రమాద హెచ్చరిక జారీ చేశారు. లోతట్టు ప్రాంతాల్లోని ప్రజలను పునరావాస కేంద్రాలకు తరలిస్తున్నట్లు కలెక్టర్‌ వెల్లడించారు.
author: 64606d9c3cd3d20007476317

title: శ్రీశైలం జలాశయానికి కొనసాగుతున్న 52,973 క్యూసెక్కుల ఇన్‌ఫ్లో, 816 అడుగులు దాటిన ప్రాజెక్టు నీటిమట్టం
content: కృష్ణా పరివాహక ప్రాంతంలో కురుస్తున్న వర్షాలకు ఉమ్మడి కర్నూలు జిల్లాలోని శ్రీశైలం ప్రాజెక్ట్‌లోకి 52,973 క్యూసెక్కుల ఇన్‌ఫ్లో వస్తున్నట్లు ప్రాజెక్ట్‌ అధికారులు తెలిపారు. ఇందులో జూరాల నుంచి 52,856 క్యూసెక్కులు, హంద్రీ నది నుంచి 117 క్యూసెక్కుల నీరు చేరుతోంది. శ్రీశైలం జలాశయం పూర్తిస్థాయి నీటిమట్టం 885 అడుగులు కాగా గురువారం ఉదయం 6 గంటల వరకు 816.20 అడుగుల నీరు నిల్వ ఉన్నట్లు అధికారులు వెల్లడించారు.
author: 64606d9c3cd3d20007476317

title: ఒక్క సబ్జెక్ట్‌లో ఫెయిలవడంతో శ్రీశైలంలో ఇంట్లో ఉరేసుకుని ఎంబీబీఎస్‌ ఫస్టియర్‌ విద్యార్థిని ఆత్మహత్య
content: ఉమ్మడి కర్నూలు జిల్లాలోని శ్రీశైలంలో మెడికో ఉరివేసుకొని ఆత్మహత్యకు పాల్పడింది. ఏపీఎస్పీడీసీఎల్ శ్రీశైలం ఏఈగా విధులు నిర్వహిస్తున్న సత్యనారాయణ కుమార్తె ధరణి బెంగళూరులో ఎంబీబీఎస్‌ మొదటి సంవత్సరం  చదువుతోంది. రెండు రోజుల క్రితం వెలువడిన పరీక్ష ఫలితాల్లో ఒక సబ్జెక్టులో ఫెయిల్‌ కావడంతో మనస్థాపంతో బుధవారం తెల్లవారుజామున ఇంట్లో బలవన్మరణానికి పాల్పడింది. పోలీసులు ఘటనాస్థలిని పరిశీలించి వివరాలు సేకరించారు.
author: 6460722f8f69d20007900ab8

title: ఈ నెల 28న చేపట్టే చలో దిల్లీ యాత్రలో పాల్గొనేందుకు నంద్యాల నుంచి ప్రత్యేక రైళ్లలో వెళ్లిన రాయలసీమ నేతలు
content: జూలై 28న జరగనున్న చలో దిల్లీ కార్యక్రమంలో పాల్గొనేందుకు ఉమ్మడి కర్నూలు జిల్లా నుంచి రాయలసీమ స్టీరింగ్‌ కమిటీ ఛైర్మన్‌ బైరెడ్డి రాజశేఖర్‌ రెడ్డి ఏర్పాటు చేసిన ప్రత్యేక రైళ్లలో ప్రజలు దిల్లీ బయలుదేరి వెళ్లారు. రాయలసీమకు నీళ్లు, నిధులు, నియామకాల్లో సమాన వాటా కోరుతూ ఈ యాత్ర చేపట్టామన్నారు. ఇక్కడ జరుగుతున్న అన్యాయాలను కేంద్ర ప్రభుత్వం దృష్టికి తీసుకెళ్లేందుకే ఆందోళన చేపడుతున్నట్లు నాయకులు తెలిపారు.
author: 6460722f8f69d20007900ab8

title: భారీ వర్షాలతో ములుగు జిల్లాలో 163వ జాతీయ రహదారికి గండి, నిలిచిపోయిన రాకపోకలు
content: భారీ వర్షాల కారణంగా ములుగు జిల్లా గోవిందరావుపేట మండలంలో 163వ జాతీయ రహదారికి గండి పడింది. హైవేపై ఉన్న బ్రిడ్జి వరదతో కోతకు గురైంది. దీంతో తాడ్వాయి, ఏటూరు నాగారం గ్రామాల మధ్య రాకపోకలు నిలిచిపోయాయి. అలాగే పస్రా గ్రామంలోని అభ్యుదయ కాలనీ వద్ద రహదారి కోతకు గురైంది. దయ్యాల వాగు సమీపంలోని ఎస్సీ కాలనీలోకి వర్షపు నీరు చేరింది. లోతట్టు ప్రాంతాల్లో ఇళ్లు నీట మునిగాయి.
author: 646072f88f69d20007900c02

title: సామర్థ్యానికి మించి వరద రావడంతో కడెం ప్రాజెక్ట్‌ పై నుంచి పారుతున్న నీరు, తెరుచుకోని నాలుగు గేట్లు
content: నిర్మల్ జిల్లాలోని కడెం ప్రాజెక్ట్ పూర్తిస్థాయి నీటి మట్టానికి (700 అడుగులు) చేరుకుంది. ప్రాజెక్టు ఇన్‌ఫ్లో సామర్థ్యం 3.5 లక్షల క్యూసెక్కులు కాగా, ప్రస్తుతం 3.8 లక్షల క్యూసెక్కుల వరద నీరు చేరుతోంది. దీంతో జలాశయం మీద నుంచి నీరు పారుతోంది. ప్రాజెక్టుకు మొత్తంగా 18 వరద గేట్లు ఉండగా, 14 గేట్ల ద్వారా 2.4 లక్షల క్యూసెక్కుల నీటిని దిగువకు విడుదల చేస్తున్నారు. మరో 4 గేట్లు తెరుచుకోవట్లేదు.
author: 6460731b8f69d20007900c03

title: Mbappé lost EA FC 24's cover photo to Haaland due to PSG: Reports
content: Kylian Mbappé lost out on being EA FC 24's cover star to Erling Haaland due to Paris Saint-Germain (PSG), according to reports. Mbappé will not extend his contract with PSG beyond June 2024.

title: Sri Lanka suffer their worst defeat on home soil in Test cricket history
content: Sri Lanka today suffered their worst defeat on home soil in Test cricket. Sri Lanka lost to Pakistan by an innings and 222 runs in Colombo. Pakistan's Abdullah Shafique won Player of the Match award for his 201. Sri Lanka's previous worst home defeat came in September 1993, when they lost by an innings and 208 runs to South Africa.
author: 5f70de9bd43821580e6d7022

title: India break multiple records, win 9th ODI in a row against West Indies
content: India beat West Indies by five wickets in the first ODI. India have won nine straight ODIs against West Indies. Kuldeep Yadav recorded best-ever ODI figures (3-2-6-4) for India in West Indies. West Indies were dismissed for 114, their lowest-ever home ODI total against India. Ravindra Jadeja broke record for taking most ODI wickets for India against West Indies (44).
author: 5f70de9bd43821580e6d7022

title: India announce their playing XI for 1st ODI against West Indies
content: Team India captain Rohit Sharma won the toss and elected to bowl first against West Indies in the first ODI in Barbados. Fast bowler Mukesh Kumar is making his ODI debut, while India's playing XI also features Shardul Thakur, Umran Malik and Kuldeep Yadav. Ishan Kishan will keep wickets for India in the match.
author: 5f70de9bd43821580e6d7022

title: Australia to bowl first in final Ashes 2023 Test, playing XIs announced
content: Australia captain Pat Cummins won the toss and elected to bowl first in the final Ashes 2023 Test at The Oval. Australia have made one change to their playing XI, with spinner Todd Murphy replacing Cameron Green. Meanwhile, England have named an unchanged playing XI for the match.
author: 5f70de9bd43821580e6d7022

title: Kuldeep records best-ever ODI bowling figures by an Indian on WI soil in just 3 overs
content: Team India spinner Kuldeep Yadav on Thursday created history by recording the best-ever ODI bowling figures by an Indian bowler on West Indies soil. Kuldeep registered figures of 3-2-6-4 in the first ODI in Barbados as West Indies were dismissed for 114 runs in 23 overs. The previous record was held by Bhuvneshwar Kumar (6-1-8-4).
author: 5f70de9bd43821580e6d7022

title: China play a T20I match for the first time, get all out for 23
content: China on Wednesday played their first-ever T20I. They faced Malaysia in an ICC Men's T20 World Cup Asia B Qualifier 2023 match. China were dismissed for 23 in 11.2 overs. Six Chinese batters were dismissed for a duck each. Malaysia's Syazrul Idrus took seven wickets in the match, becoming the first-ever bowler to take a seven-for in men's T20I cricket.
author: 5f70de9bd43821580e6d7022

title: Malaysia's Syazrul Idrus breaks world record for taking most wickets in a T20I match
content: Malaysia fast bowler Syazrul Idrus has broken the world record for taking most wickets in a men's T20I match. The 32-year-old picked up seven wickets in his team's ICC Men's T20 World Cup Asia B Qualifier match against China. Idrus registered figures of 4-1-8-7. Idrus bowled 20 dot deliveries in his spell.
author: 5f70de9bd43821580e6d7022

title: China get all out for 26 in T20 World Cup Qualifier
content: China were dismissed for 26 runs in their T20 World Cup Qualifier match against Thailand in Kuala Lumpur. Six of China's batters were dismissed for a duck each. Seven of their batters were bowled out in the match. In their first T20 World Cup Qualifier match, China were dismissed for 23 against Malaysia.
author: 5f70de9bd43821580e6d7022

title: टी20 विश्व कप क्वॉलिफायर में 26 रन पर ऑल-आउट हुआ चीन
content: कुआलालंपुर (मलेशिया) में थाईलैंड के खिलाफ टी20 विश्व कप क्वॉलिफायर मैच में चीन 26 रन पर ऑल-आउट हो गया। चीन के 6 बल्लेबाज़ डक पर आउट हुए और उसके 7 बल्लेबाज़ बोल्ड आउट हुए। इससे पूर्व अपने पहले टी20 विश्व कप क्वॉलिफायर मैच में चीन की पारी मलेशिया के खिलाफ 23 रन पर सिमट गई थी।
author: 5f70e895d43821580e6d7076

title: भारत ने वेस्टइंडीज़ के खिलाफ जीता लगातार 9वां वनडे मैच, तोड़े कई रिकॉर्ड
content: भारत ने बारबाडोस में पहले वनडे में वेस्टइंडीज़ को 5 विकेट से हरा दिया है। वनडे में यह वेस्टइंडीज़ के खिलाफ भारत की लगातार 9वीं जीत है। मैच में कुलदीप यादव ने वेस्टइंडीज़ में वनडे में किसी भारतीय के सर्वश्रेष्ठ (3-2-6-4) गेंदबाज़ी आंकड़े दर्ज किए और वेस्टइंडीज़ अपने घर पर भारत के खिलाफ सबसे कम स्कोर (114-रन) पर ऑलआउट हुआ।
author: 62bec075573ea25553962618

title: भारत ने वेस्टइंडीज़ के खिलाफ पहले वनडे के लिए किया प्लेइंग इलेवन का एलान
content: भारत ने बारबाडोस में वेस्टइंडीज़ के खिलाफ पहले वनडे में टॉस जीतकर गेंदबाज़ी करने का फैसला किया है। मैच में तेज़ गेंदबाज़ मुकेश कुमार भारत की तरफ से वनडे डेब्यू कर रहे हैं और भारतीय प्लेइंग इलेवन में शार्दुल ठाकुर, उमरान मलिक और कुलदीप यादव शामिल हैं। भारतीय प्लेइंग इलेवन में विकेटकीपर इशान किशन को भी शामिल किया गया है।
author: 62bec075573ea25553962618

title: कुलदीप ने दर्ज किए वेस्टइंडीज़ में वनडे में किसी भारतीय के सर्वश्रेष्ठ गेंदबाज़ी आंकड़े
content: भारतीय स्पिनर कुलदीप यादव ने गुरुवार को वेस्टइंडीज़ में किसी भारतीय द्वारा वनडे में सर्वश्रेष्ठ गेंदबाज़ी आंकड़े दर्ज कर इतिहास रच दिया। बारबाडोस में पहले वनडे में कुलदीप ने 3-2-6-4 के आंकड़े दर्ज किए जिसके बाद वेस्टइंडीज़ 23 ओवर में 114 रन पर ऑलआउट हुआ। पिछला रिकॉर्ड भुवनेश्वर कुमार के नाम दर्ज था जिन्होंने 6-1-8-4 के आंकड़े दर्ज किए थे।
author: 62bec075573ea25553962618

title: What is 'juice jacking', scam done through public charging ports?
content: 'Juice jacking' scam occurs when fraudsters con people with help of charging ports in public places. It involves malware injection directly into user's device while it charges, giving scammers control over the victim's device. The malicious software or hardware can start harvesting sensitive data from the connected device. The RBI has also cautioned about the scam in its booklet.
author: 5f70de9bd43821580e6d7022

title: Man releases snake in govt office as complaints go unheard in Hyd; video surfaces
content: A man in Hyderabad's Alwal released a snake into a ward office of the Greater Hyderabad Municipal Corporation after his complaints about the snake entering his house were allegedly ignored. A video of the incident surfaced online, in which the snake is seen lying on a table in the government office. The reptile reportedly entered the man's house amid rains.
author: 5f70e896573ea2734e3862cc

title: Pak SC rejects Khan's plea to stay proceedings in Toshakhana case
content: Pakistan's Supreme Court on Wednesday rejected the ousted PM Imran Khan's plea to stay the criminal proceedings against him in Toshakhana corruption case, which revolves around illegally selling state gifts. Khan had reportedly approached the apex court after being denied relief in the corruption case by the Islamabad High Court. The Toshakhana case was filed against Khan last year.
author: 5f770f2c573ea22260e38d55

title: Byju would travel 9 cities in a week, take classes in stadiums to teach Maths: Wife
content: BYJU's Co-founder & CEO Byju Raveendran would travel to nine cities in a week and take classes in packed stadiums to teach students Maths, his wife and other Co-founder Divya Gokulnath said. She was recollecting the start of the company as BYJU's Classes in 2007. \We hired a stadium. It was packed to capacity
author: NEWS

title: Mother sold all real estate after it took 2 yrs to evict a tenant: Capitalmind CEO
content: Bengaluru-based Capitalmind CEO Deepak Shenoy revealed that it took his mother two years to get a court order for evicting a tenant who didn't pay rent after the first month. He added his mother sold all real estate after this incident. \More money has been made in markets with far lesser hassle
author: \" he said."

title: एचसी ने सर्विस चार्ज नियम के उल्लंघन पर रेस्टोरेंट असोसिएशन्स पर लगाया ₹1 लाख का जुर्माना
content: दिल्ली हाईकोर्ट ने नैशनल रेस्टोरेंट असोसिएशन ऑफ इंडिया (एनआरएआई) और द फेडरेशन ऑफ होटल ऐंड रेस्टोरेंट असोसिएशन ऑफ इंडिया (एफएचआरएआई) को सर्विस चार्ज के नियमों का पालन न करने पर ₹1-₹1 लाख का जुर्माना लगाया है। कोर्ट ने एनआरएआई और एफएचआरएआई को अनिवार्य सर्विस चार्ज लेने वाले रेस्टोरेंट्स की जानकारी से जुड़ा हलफनामा दायर करने को कहा है।
author: 619b861f573ea266d0ebff94

title: US family makes $7 mn via state recycling scheme, accused of fraud
content: A family has been charged with fraud for pocketing $7.6 million by exploiting California's recycling scheme. Over an eight-month period, the Riverside family recycled 178 tons of beverage containers, brought from Arizona state, to exploit the scheme, which only applies to beverage containers purchased in California. California offers five or 10 cents for each beverage container that is recycled.
author: 61a77175d43821182161b35e

title: Indonesia temporarily halts Musk's X.com over gambling, porn laws
content: Billionaire Elon Musk's X.com domain, which redirects to Twitter, has been temporarily halted in Indonesia over gambling and porn laws. Indonesian Communication Ministry said the domain was previously used by sites that didn't adhere to laws against content like porn and gambling. Musk's X.com will send a letter to say that the domain will be used for Twitter, it added.
author: 61a77175d43821182161b35e

title: Peak XV to cut BYJU'S valuation over lack of transparency: Report
content: BYJU'S investor Peak XV is planning to markdown the valuation of the edtech startup significantly due to lack of visibility on audited financials, The Economic Times reported. Peak XV reportedly told its own investors that its executive GV Ravishankar resigned from BYJU'S board as BYJU'S leadership was unwilling to follow advice. Investor Prosus also made similar claims over board exit.
author: 61a77175d43821182161b35e

title: Govt cracks down on apps showing incorrect maps of India: Report
content: The Electronics and IT Ministry and Survey of India are cracking down on apps that have been depicting India's map incorrectly. Last month, a notice was issued to Google after an app on Play Store, World Map Quiz, depicted Jammu and Kashmir and Ladakh incorrectly. Another notice was issued to Google regarding a game depicting an incorrect map of India.
author: 61a77175d43821182161b35e

title: BlackRock to re-enter India through JV with Jio Financial Services
content: BlackRock will be re-entering India through a 50:50 joint venture with Jio Financial Services, which will create \Jio BlackRock\". Both partners plan an initial investment of $150 million and aim to together provide tech-enabled and affordable investment solutions to Indian investors. The announcement comes days after Jio Financial Services was demerged from Reliance Industries."
author: 61a77175d43821182161b35e

title: Peak XV says lack of transparency led to BYJU'S board exit: Report
content: The second-biggest institutional shareholder in BYJU'S, Peak XV, said its executive GV Ravishankar left the edtech startup's board due to lack of transparency, Moneycontrol reported. BYJU'S leadership was unwilling to follow advice and suggestions related to corporate governance, legal and operational matters, Peak XV said. Ravishankar wasn't able to discharge his duties as an investor, it added.
author: 61a77175d43821182161b35e

title: Tata Motors board approves cancellation of 'A' Ordinary Shares
content: Tata Motors' board has approved a Scheme of Arrangement for the cancellation of 'A' ordinary shares and issue of seven ordinary shares for every 10 'A' ordinary shares held by shareholders. 'A' ordinary shares carry 1/10th of voting rights of ordinary shares and are entitled to five percentage points higher dividend. They currently trade at 43% discount to ordinary shares.
author: 61a77175d43821182161b35e

title: Hero Motors to raise ₹1,500 cr via IPO, has picked 3 banks: Report
content: Hero Motors is likely to raise ₹1,500 crore via an IPO, for which the auto component maker has picked three investment banks, The Economic Times reported. ICICI Securities is expected to lead manage the proposed public issue, which the company has been preparing for since the last 18 months. Hero Motors appointed Deloitte Haskins and Sells as its auditor.
author: 61a77175d43821182161b35e

title: Myntra to eliminate 50 roles in restructuring move
content: Myntra is likely to eliminate about 50 roles in a restructuring move that will impact people across the organisation, which a spokesperson for the online fashion startup confirmed without providing specifics. \Wherever a small number of roles may be impacted
newsType: we offer our employees an opportunity to alternate positions...within the organisation as well as group companies
author: \" Myntra said."

title: Rahul Yadav-led 4B Networks to enter arbitration with Info Edge
content: Info Edge hasn't received crucial information from 4B Networks, led by sacked Housing.com CEO Rahul Yadav, despite repeated requests as part of forensic audit the company initiated against the startup. Info Edge has sent a legal notice to 4B Networks and both firms will be entering arbitration proceedings. A ₹288-crore investment in 4B Networks was previously written-off by Info Edge.
author: 61a77175d43821182161b35e

title: Tata Motors board approves cancellation of 'A' Ordinary Shares
content: Tata Motors' board has approved a Scheme of Arrangement for the cancellation of 'A' ordinary shares and issue of seven ordinary shares for every 10 'A' ordinary shares held by shareholders. 'A' ordinary shares carry 1/10th of voting rights of ordinary shares and are entitled to five percentage points higher dividend. They currently trade at 43% discount to ordinary shares.
author: 61a77175d43821182161b35e

title: 25 startups being evaluated for chip design subsidy scheme: MoS IT
content: Minister of State for IT Rajeev Chandrasekhar said the government is currently evaluating 25 startups for availing government financial support under the semiconductor design subsidy scheme. The incentives and support are set to be extended to domestic companies, startups and MSMEs over a five-year period. \If there's need...to intervene and create more PLI-type schemes
author: \" he said."

title: Delhi HC fines restaurant associations ₹1 lakh over service charge order
content: Delhi HC has directed the National Restaurant Association of India (NRAI) and The Federation of Hotel & Restaurant Associations of India (FHRAI) to pay ₹1,00,000 each as costs for complete non-compliance of service charge directions. As per the order dated April 12, NRAI and FHRAI were directed to submit specific affidavits regarding the percentage of members imposing mandatory service charges.
author: 61de9224d438211e6ea8e7d5

title: I am what I am because of IIT-Bombay: Infosys Co-founder Nilekani
content: Infosys Co-founder Nandan Nilekani said he owes all his achievements to his alma mater IIT-Bombay. IIT-Bombay named its iconic main building 'Nandan Nilekani Main Building' in recognition of Nilekani's philanthropic support to the institute. \A special day for me: Returned to @iitbombay 50 years after I first entered the institution. I'm what I am because of IIT-Bombay
author: NEWS

title: Grain sales to states under OMSS stopped to maintain stock: Govt
content: Centre said it had discontinued wheat and rice sales to states under Open Market Sale Scheme (OMSS) from June 13 to maintain adequate buffer stock and control price rise. Karnataka, West Bengal and Tamil Nadu requested wheat and rice under OMSS (D) Policy, which was not acceded to due to the discontinuation of the sale, MoS Sadhvi Niranjan Jyoti said.
author: 62dabeebd438213aabd919fa

title: X asks brands to spend $1,000/month on ads or lose verified status
content: X has now mandated that brands spend at least $1,000/month on ads or risk losing their verified status, The Wall Street Journal reported. Musk said a \moderately high bar\" for a verified organisation on the platform was to keep
newsType: \"scammers\" from creating \"millions of accounts\". X is reportedly offering a 50% discount on all new ad bookings through July 31."
author: NEWS

title: Jio Financial Services, BlackRock to form asset management JV
content: Jio Financial Services Limited and BlackRock announced an agreement to create \Jio BlackRock
newsType: \" a 50:50 joint venture. Each partner plans an initial investment of $150 million and they aim to provide tech-enabled and affordable investment solutions to Indian investors. The joint venture will begin operations once it receives regulatory approvals and will have its independent management team."
author: NEWS

title: Adani Transmission renamed to Adani Energy Solutions
content: Adani Transmission on Thursday said it has renamed itself Adani Energy Solutions Limited with immediate effect. The company has submitted the requisite documents with the stock exchanges in relation to the same. A board meeting of the company is scheduled for July 31 to approve and announce the results for the first quarter ended June.
author: 62dabeebd438213aabd919fa

title: ECB hikes interest rate to 4.25%, highest level since May 2001
content: The European Central Bank (ECB) on Thursday raised borrowing costs by 0.25 percentage points to 4.25%, taking a key rate to its highest level since May 2001 as its battle against surging inflation reached the one-year mark. The decision to hike rates for the ninth straight time is part of an attempt to bring down inflation.
author: 62dabeebd438213aabd919fa

title: NCLT refuses to restrain Go First from using leased aircraft
content: The National Company Law Tribunal (NCLT) on Wednesday refused to restrain Go First from using leased aircraft for its operations and said those aircraft are essential to keep Go First as a going concern company. \The DGCA has not deregistered the aircraft
newsType: which means that they are available to Go First for use to resume operations\"
author: NCLT's order noted."

title: Real estate agents can't operate from homes: Delhi-RERA Chairman
content: Delhi-Real Estate Regulatory Authority (RERA) Chairman Anand Kumar said real estate agents cannot operate from a residential address and it is mandatory for them to maintain a commercial office for which property tax has been paid. \Both planned and unplanned areas are covered under RERA and projects in these areas have to be registered under the Act
author: NEWS

title: Citi India consumer business integration on track: Axis Bank MD
content: Integration of Citibank India consumer business remains well on track with around 3,200 Citi employees now part of the bank, Axis Bank MD and CEO Amitabh Chaudhry told shareholders. \Our interactions with several high-value customers suggest their acknowledgement of the seamless transition
author: Axis Bank said it completed the acquisition of Citibank's consumer business."

title: Meta, govt ink MoU to partner on AI, emerging technologies
content: Meta has signed an initial pact with the Centre to partner on artificial intelligence and other emerging technologies. \'India AI' is an exciting programme and with close collaboration between government and industry
newsType: we can strengthen India's digital leadership and help to ensure AI tools are built for India's unique needs
author: \" Meta's Global Affairs President Nick Clegg said."

title: Cabinet approves ₹5,000 crore scheme for pharma companies: Report
content: The Union Cabinet approved the Promotion of Research and Innovation in Pharma-MedTech (PRIP) scheme to boost research and innovation in the sector, CNBC Awaaz reported citing sources. Nearly ₹5,000 crore will be spent in five years under the scheme and companies will be given incentives for research. Seven centres of excellence will be opened for research in the pharma sector.
author: 62dabeebd438213aabd919fa

title: AIX Connect gets approval to fly under Air India Express brand
content: Tata Group-owned AIX Connect, operating as AirAsia India, said it has received regulatory approval to operate its flights under the 'Air India Express' branding. Air India Express and AirAsia India are now permitted to jointly promote, sell and operate their services as 'Air India Express'. Air India, Air India Express, Vistara and AirAsia India are currently part of AIX Connect.
author: 62dabeebd438213aabd919fa

title: India to become key chip player in 10 yrs with $10 bn PLI: MoS IT
content: India will become a key player in the global semiconductor supply chain in the next decade with $10 billion of production-linked incentives compared to China's three decades of progress, MoS IT Rajeev Chandrasekhar said. He added there is \not one person in...semiconductor global ecosystem\" that doesn't see India as \"a very credible...destination for semiconductor investments and innovation\"."
author: 62dabeebd438213aabd919fa

title: PMO probing Chinese stainless steel dumping: Jindal Stainless MD
content: Prime Minister's Office (PMO) has launched a probe into the potential dumping of Chinese stainless steel products into the country, Jindal Stainless MD Abhyuday Jindal said. Stainless steel producers have petitioned to impose a countervailing duty on Chinese stainless steel products. Jindal added that Chinese stainless steel products have taken over around 30% of India's domestic market.
author: 62dabeebd438213aabd919fa

title: I won Pepsi contest, Aishwarya Rai visited 'home': Ex-Swiggy COO
content: Ex-Swiggy COO Vivek Sunder shared that in the early 1990s, he had won a slogan-writing contest by Pepsi which led to former Miss World Aishwarya Rai visiting his \house\". As the news spread about the 15-minute meeting
newsType: Sunder said he realised that Pepsi basically marketed itself by making customers work. Sunder then decided to pursue an MBA course."
author: NEWS

title: अदाणी ट्रांसमिशन का नाम बदलकर किया गया अदाणी एनर्जी सॉल्यूशंस
content: गौतम अदाणी के अगुआई वाले अदाणी समूह की कंपनी अदाणी ट्रांसमिशन का नाम बदलकर अदाणी एनर्जी सॉल्यूशंस कर दिया गया है। इस मामले में कंपनी पंजीयक से ज़रूरी मंज़ूरी मिलने के बाद यह कदम उठाया गया है। गौरतलब है कि कंपनी की देश के 14 राज्यों में उपस्थिति है और यह देश की सबसे बड़ी प्राइवेट ट्रांसमिशन कंपनी है।
author: 619b85fa573ea266d0ebfee2

title: 15 दिन में तेलंगाना के किसान ने टमाटर बेचकर कमाए ₹2 करोड़
content: देशभर में टमाटर के कीमतों में वृद्धि के बीच मेडक (तेलंगाना) के बी. महिपाल रेड्डी नामक किसान ने टमाटर बेचकर पिछले 15 दिन में लगभग ₹2 करोड़ कमाए हैं। रेड्डी ने कहा कि उनके खेतों में अब भी ₹1 करोड़ की टमाटर की फसल बची है। राज्य के मुख्यमंत्री के. चंद्रशेखर राव ने इसको लेकर रेड्डी की सराहना की है।
author: 619b85fa573ea266d0ebfee2

title: क्या होंगी राजस्थान में आयोजित होने वाली राष्ट्रीय हथकरघा प्रदर्शनी की विशेषताएं?
content: जयपुर (राजस्थान) के जवाहर कला केंद्र व राजस्थान इंटरनैशनल सेंटर में आगामी 3 अगस्त से 7 अगस्त तक राष्ट्रीय हथकरघा प्रदर्शनी का आयोजन किया जाएगा। इस प्रदर्शनी में हथकरघा और खादी उत्पादों को प्रदर्शित करने के लिए 80 स्टॉल लगाए जाएंगे। 10 राष्ट्रीय पुरस्कार विजेता बुनकर भी इस प्रदर्शनी में भाग लेंगे और अपनी श्रेष्ठ कृतियों का प्रदर्शन करेंगे।
author: 619b861f573ea266d0ebff94

title: 2019 से जून 2023 तक वंदे भारत ट्रेन पर पथराव को लेकर 151 लोग गिरफ्तार किए गए: सरकार
content: केंद्रीय रेल मंत्री अश्विनी वैष्णव ने बुधवार को लोकसभा में बताया कि 2019 से जून 2023 के बीच वंदे भारत ट्रेन पर पथराव की घटनाओं में शामिल 151 लोग गिरफ्तार किए गए हैं। उन्होंने बताया कि पथराव की इन घटनाओं में रेलवे को ₹55.60 लाख का नुकसान हुआ है। बकौल वैष्णव, इन घटनाओं में कोई यात्री हताहत नहीं हुआ।
author: 619b861f573ea266d0ebff94

title: बीते 9 वर्षों में रेल दुर्घटनाओं में 781 लोगों की हुई मौत, 1,545 लोग हुए घायल: सरकार
content: रेल मंत्री अश्विनी वैष्णव ने लोकसभा में बताया है कि वित्त वर्ष 2014-15 से 2022-23 के बीच रेल दुर्घटनाओं में 781 लोगों की मौत हुई और 1,545 लोग घायल हुए हैं। वैष्णव ने बताया कि इस अवधि में कुल 638 परिणामी रेल दुर्घटनाएं हुई हैं। बकौल वैष्णव, सरकार ने रेलपथ और सिग्नल प्रणाली में कई सुधार किए हैं।
author: 619b861f573ea266d0ebff94

title: असली लूट तो पीएम मोदी ने लाल सिलिंडर को ₹1150 में बेचकर मचा रखी है: राजस्थान सीएम
content: राजस्थान के मुख्यमंत्री अशोक गहलोत ने गुरुवार को प्रधानमंत्री नरेंद्र मोदी के बयान 'कांग्रेस का मतलब ही लूट की दुकान और झूठ का बाज़ार है' पर प्रतिक्रिया दी। उन्होंने कहा, \असली लूट तो पीएम मोदी ने लाल सिलिंडर को ₹1

title: बर्खास्त मंत्री राजेंद्र गुढ़ा के खिलाफ मानहानि का केस करेंगे राजस्थान के मंत्री महेश जोशी
content: राजस्थान सरकार द्वारा मंत्री पद से बर्खास्त राजेंद्र गुढ़ा के कांग्रेस नेताओं को 'दुष्कर्मी' कहने को लेकर राज्य सरकार में जलदाय मंत्री महेश जोशी ने बुधवार को कहा कि वह गुढ़ा के खिलाफ मानहानि का केस करेंगे। उन्होंने कहा, \इस पर वकीलों की राय ले रहा हूं उसके बाद केस करूंगा..जो आरोप उन्होंने लगाए हैं उसके जवाब उन्हें देने होंगे।\""

title: दिल्ली हाईकोर्ट ने शहर में तेज़ाब की बिक्री पर पूर्ण प्रतिबंध लगाने से किया इनकार
content: दिल्ली हाईकोर्ट ने तेज़ाब हमले की पीड़िता की याचिका पर सुनवाई करते हुए गुरुवार को तेज़ाब पर पूर्ण प्रतिबंध लगाने से इनकार कर दिया। हाईकोर्ट ने कहा, \इससे उन कारोबारों व लोगों पर प्रतिकूल असर पड़ सकता है जिन्हें वैध कामों के लिए इसकी ज़रूरत है।\" कोर्ट ने इसकी बिक्री के लिए मौजूदा नियमों को लागू करने के निर्देश दिए।"
